1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,830
The most entertaining suspense
that predicts love.

2
00:00:02,830 --> 00:00:04,600
Love line prediction game, Heart Signal.

3
00:00:04,600 --> 00:00:08,940
Five people with sharp romance
radars have gathered.

4
00:00:08,940 --> 00:00:11,700
[The panel of five people is here]

5
00:00:11,700 --> 00:00:15,780
Wu Yeol and Yu Gyeong's date
got people talking.

6
00:00:15,780 --> 00:00:18,850
I just remember their hands locking.
It was so romantic.

7
00:00:18,850 --> 00:00:21,800
You know how it
doesn't just happen immediately.

8
00:00:21,800 --> 00:00:25,670
It started like this.
They started touching fingers.

9
00:00:25,670 --> 00:00:28,090
There were a few other steps
before we got there.

10
00:00:28,090 --> 00:00:30,500
- That's really...
- I need to watch it again.

11
00:00:30,500 --> 00:00:34,230
It was so funny that while holding
hands, they kept a straight face.

12
00:00:34,230 --> 00:00:37,670
They didn't know we could see the hands.

13
00:00:37,670 --> 00:00:40,850
They were acting differently
with their faces.

14
00:00:40,850 --> 00:00:43,320
That made it even more awkward.

15
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:46,280
We saw everything right here.

16
00:00:46,280 --> 00:00:48,430
To me, it was Tsuki's tears.

17
00:00:48,430 --> 00:00:50,240
- Seriously.
- I don't remember the rest.

18
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:52,500
Her face actually got puffy then.

19
00:00:52,500 --> 00:00:55,880
- Seriously.
- Even her nose got puffed up.

20
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:58,090
My eyelashes fell out, too.

21
00:00:58,090 --> 00:00:59,710
She got emotionally invested.

22
00:00:59,710 --> 00:01:03,260
I thought I was Yu Gyeong in that moment.

23
00:01:03,260 --> 00:01:05,700
I got totally sucked in.

24
00:01:05,700 --> 00:01:10,390
I was like, "It finally happened."
I was totally into it.

25
00:01:10,390 --> 00:01:14,340
- I started crying without realizing.
- I was so surprised.

26
00:01:14,340 --> 00:01:17,850
And Wu Yeol's attitude definitely changed.

27
00:01:17,850 --> 00:01:21,500
At the bar, he said
he pretended to be mature.

28
00:01:21,500 --> 00:01:26,400
He said he acted like that because
of his new situation living in Seoul.

29
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:28,840
He said he was defensive.

30
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:31,760
He was talking to Yu Gyeong honestly.

31
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,310
I could tell he really likes her.

32
00:01:33,310 --> 00:01:38,240
He let go of everything for Yu Gyeong.

33
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:40,950
He realized
it brings him peace and happiness.

34
00:01:40,950 --> 00:01:43,680
I might be delusional, but...

35
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:47,690
I thought Heart Signal might have
captured their first love.

36
00:01:47,690 --> 00:01:49,490
This might be their first love.

37
00:01:49,490 --> 00:01:53,210
And Seong Min and Min Ju had a date.

38
00:01:53,210 --> 00:01:57,910
She tried to make Seong Min feel
comfortable once again.

39
00:01:57,910 --> 00:02:03,090
He said a few things
that disarmed us a bit, too.

40
00:02:03,090 --> 00:02:06,610
I didn't realize you were stressed about me.

41
00:02:06,610 --> 00:02:10,110
Of everything he has said,

42
00:02:10,110 --> 00:02:15,170
that was the most truthful and considerate.

43
00:02:15,170 --> 00:02:18,120
We found it satisfactory, too.

44
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:21,520
Lastly, Jun Hyeon and So Yun had a date.

45
00:02:21,520 --> 00:02:23,550
These two always have good chemistry.

46
00:02:23,550 --> 00:02:25,580
Thinking now,

47
00:02:25,580 --> 00:02:28,560
both Jun Hyeon and So Yun always have

48
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:31,110
good chemistry with other people.

49
00:02:31,110 --> 00:02:34,630
That's why their chemistry was so great.

50
00:02:34,630 --> 00:02:39,000
It's finally Heart Signal 5's
final decision day.

51
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:40,670
I just hope things stay this way.

52
00:02:40,670 --> 00:02:44,340
I have never felt such intense feelings.

53
00:02:44,340 --> 00:02:47,760
I didn't think I could get so
into other people's relationships.

54
00:02:47,760 --> 00:02:51,500
I didn't think I would at my age.

55
00:02:51,500 --> 00:02:53,850
[Excited for the end of Heart Signal 5]

56
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,630
Gunsan was nice.

57
00:02:56,630 --> 00:02:59,440
- I ate all I wanted.
- Me, too.

58
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:02,490
Honestly, I really enjoyed the pork belly.

59
00:03:02,490 --> 00:03:04,800
It was so good.

60
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:06,250
What does that mean?

61
00:03:06,250 --> 00:03:09,910
"Honestly, I really enjoyed it."

62
00:03:09,910 --> 00:03:14,190
- Do you like pork ribs?
- Of course, I do.

63
00:03:17,440 --> 00:03:20,050
[Car wash]

64
00:03:21,190 --> 00:03:25,100
- Do you like to get a car wash?
- I do.

65
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:27,640
I don't like it.

66
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:32,700
I prefer it when it's dirty.

67
00:03:32,700 --> 00:03:36,130
You're in trouble. I'll get my lint roller.

68
00:03:36,130 --> 00:03:38,400
I'll do intense lint rolling.

69
00:03:39,330 --> 00:03:43,630
Did you notice my right shoulder
keeps dropping?

70
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:47,590
You can't just do this.

71
00:03:53,270 --> 00:03:55,170
[Staring]

72
00:04:00,230 --> 00:04:02,530
I mean...

73
00:04:04,830 --> 00:04:09,120
[Taking a nap after the tiring trip]

74
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:11,660
[Meanwhile, in Jun Hyeon and So Yun's car]

75
00:04:11,660 --> 00:04:14,400
Seo Won and I share something very similar.

76
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:18,790
I have just two friends I hang out with.

77
00:04:18,790 --> 00:04:21,980
He said he only had three or four friends.

78
00:04:21,980 --> 00:04:23,760
And here's another thing.

79
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:29,450
I send tons of reel videos
to those two friends.

80
00:04:29,450 --> 00:04:33,280
I'm the only one talking.
He apparently does the same.

81
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:39,330
Seo Won and I say "Love you"
to each other before bed.

82
00:04:39,330 --> 00:04:41,660
I mean it.

83
00:04:41,660 --> 00:04:44,290
We say "Love you" and go to bed.

84
00:04:44,290 --> 00:04:46,070
[The two men's affectionate bedtime routine]

85
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:51,240
[They're back at Signal House]

86
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:54,630
- We're finally back.
- Hello.

87
00:04:54,630 --> 00:04:59,220
- We're probably really late.
- We are probably the last ones to arrive.

88
00:04:59,220 --> 00:05:01,990
[Wu Yeol and Yu Gyeong arrive last]

89
00:05:01,990 --> 00:05:04,730
Do you want this?

90
00:05:04,730 --> 00:05:06,200
What's this?

91
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:09,040
One is to keep, and the other one is trash.

92
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:11,360
[All tenants arrived at Signal House]

93
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:14,140
Take this with you.

94
00:05:14,140 --> 00:05:17,230
[Thinking]

95
00:05:17,230 --> 00:05:19,400
[Capybara plushie]

96
00:05:20,070 --> 00:05:23,430
I like capybaras.

97
00:05:23,430 --> 00:05:27,360
[Switching immediately]

98
00:05:29,330 --> 00:05:32,980
[A plushie with loose stitches]

99
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:38,930
No, I'll stitch this myself.

100
00:05:38,930 --> 00:05:41,660
You really won't let me have it.

101
00:05:45,830 --> 00:05:46,850
[Running]

102
00:05:52,950 --> 00:05:54,470
Hi.

103
00:05:54,470 --> 00:05:56,010
Hi.

104
00:06:00,070 --> 00:06:01,140
[Running]

105
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:06,720
She was in a cutesy mode today.

106
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:09,580
She was so funny when we did paragliding.

107
00:06:09,580 --> 00:06:12,200
All I could hear in the sky was her voice.

108
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,930
She kept screaming so loudly.

109
00:06:13,930 --> 00:06:16,780
[So Yun in that intense moment]

110
00:06:16,780 --> 00:06:19,730
She was like, "Our tailbone will break!"

111
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:23,710
She was worried about them
breaking while landing.

112
00:06:24,620 --> 00:06:26,530
[Staring]

113
00:06:27,650 --> 00:06:30,610
[What's Seo Won thinking about?]

114
00:06:30,610 --> 00:06:34,950
[Send a video message to someone
you cherish the most at Signal House]

115
00:06:34,950 --> 00:06:41,500
Just because
I have feelings for you, Seo Won,

116
00:06:41,500 --> 00:06:45,220
I hope you don't treat me cautiously

117
00:06:45,220 --> 00:06:49,290
or think we can't go back
to how we were before.

118
00:06:49,290 --> 00:06:54,020
Keep joking around, tease me,

119
00:06:54,020 --> 00:06:58,580
and make fun of me.
That's what I like about you.

120
00:06:58,580 --> 00:07:02,850
I apologize if I pressured you by any chance.

121
00:07:02,850 --> 00:07:04,570
But...

122
00:07:06,350 --> 00:07:11,450
I had unforgettable moments here,
thanks to you.

123
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:16,360
I'm so grateful for that.

124
00:07:17,890 --> 00:07:22,070
[So Yun's last Self Talk was recorded]

125
00:07:22,070 --> 00:07:23,790
She's done.

126
00:07:27,430 --> 00:07:29,410
[Staring]

127
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:33,390
You scared me.

128
00:07:33,390 --> 00:07:36,040
What?

129
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:38,450
- Have a seat.
- Have a seat.

130
00:07:38,450 --> 00:07:41,240
Why did you stare at me like that?

131
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,950
- How was it?
- Ouch.

132
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:44,850
- Have you been well?
- Have I been well?

133
00:07:44,850 --> 00:07:47,990
- Did you have a nice trip?
- I sure did.

134
00:07:49,450 --> 00:07:51,860
I'll be right back.

135
00:07:51,860 --> 00:07:56,310
[Send a video message to someone
you cherish the most at Signal House]

136
00:07:56,310 --> 00:08:00,400
[Seo Won's Self Talk]

137
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:13,240
[He's getting emotional]

138
00:08:20,990 --> 00:08:25,550
Let's say your first date was

139
00:08:25,550 --> 00:08:29,170
someone other than Gyu Ri.

140
00:08:29,170 --> 00:08:32,020
Do you think the result would have changed?

141
00:08:43,190 --> 00:08:45,110
How about you?

142
00:08:45,110 --> 00:08:48,780
If you chose a different person to talk to

143
00:08:48,780 --> 00:08:52,310
and had dates with someone else,

144
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:55,550
do you think the result would have changed?

145
00:08:56,580 --> 00:08:59,580
The process might have been
different, but not the result.

146
00:09:06,790 --> 00:09:08,410
How cool.

147
00:09:09,270 --> 00:09:12,190
[Seo Won is feeling conflicted]

148
00:09:15,460 --> 00:09:17,510
He's out. He's out. He's out.

149
00:09:18,770 --> 00:09:19,760
[Glued to the window]

150
00:09:23,830 --> 00:09:26,430
Gosh. Gosh.

151
00:09:31,620 --> 00:09:32,200
[Worried]

152
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:38,140
Happy Cola.

153
00:09:38,140 --> 00:09:41,510
[Happy Cola flavored jelly]

154
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:46,110
[So Yun is caring for Seo Won,
who is looking sad]

155
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:47,720
[Whine]

156
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:49,710
[He is responding jokingly]

157
00:09:49,710 --> 00:09:52,330
That stuff works.

158
00:09:52,330 --> 00:09:54,840
It lives up to its name. Happy Cola.

159
00:09:57,890 --> 00:10:02,900
[Can all tenants have a happy ending?]

160
00:10:02,900 --> 00:10:08,970
[The last night at Signal House has passed]

161
00:10:08,970 --> 00:10:11,880
[Final decision day]

162
00:10:11,880 --> 00:10:13,490
[It's their last morning at Signal House]

163
00:10:13,490 --> 00:10:14,550
What's this?

164
00:10:14,550 --> 00:10:16,460
This? Write down what you want for dinner.

165
00:10:16,460 --> 00:10:18,380
The dishes we want to have?

166
00:10:18,380 --> 00:10:21,420
[They lived together for 25 days]

167
00:10:21,420 --> 00:10:24,160
What's this? Dinner request?

168
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:25,930
How cute.

169
00:10:28,340 --> 00:10:31,480
[They created memories each day]

170
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,130
[They cooked together for the first time]

171
00:10:33,130 --> 00:10:34,840
- How did you shape it like that?
- This is so...

172
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:38,350
[They shared love through meals]

173
00:10:38,350 --> 00:10:40,530
[It was awkward at first]

174
00:10:40,530 --> 00:10:42,640
- Thanks for the meal.
- This is how it feels.

175
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:46,100
[Warmth]

176
00:10:46,100 --> 00:10:49,090
[and excitement continued]

177
00:10:49,090 --> 00:10:51,470
[Now, we became friends]

178
00:10:51,470 --> 00:10:52,920
What's this?

179
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:55,630
- What's with the fried rice?
- Who made this?

180
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:56,770
Call the police.

181
00:10:56,770 --> 00:10:58,890
[Naturally caring for each other]

182
00:10:58,890 --> 00:11:00,240
It's delicious.

183
00:11:00,240 --> 00:11:05,350
[We got used to being together]

184
00:11:06,950 --> 00:11:10,070
[The end of winter is approaching]

185
00:11:11,070 --> 00:11:14,840
[What decision will we end up making?]

186
00:11:19,390 --> 00:11:20,730
[Smiling]

187
00:11:20,730 --> 00:11:22,820
[Yu Gyeong and Seong Min's chat]

188
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:23,900
What is it?

189
00:11:23,900 --> 00:11:26,780
- You clean up well.
- What does that mean?

190
00:11:26,780 --> 00:11:29,800
- You look well.
- Do I? I got a lot of sleep.

191
00:11:29,800 --> 00:11:32,680
- Really?
- You match the house today.

192
00:11:32,680 --> 00:11:34,070
- Really?
- Yes.

193
00:11:34,070 --> 00:11:35,430
I got all dolled up today.

194
00:11:35,430 --> 00:11:38,430
You fit the house for some reason,
especially the lace.

195
00:11:38,430 --> 00:11:41,050
- She looks like the owner of the house.
- So cute.

196
00:11:41,900 --> 00:11:43,930
Thank you.

197
00:11:48,780 --> 00:11:51,370
The flame is dying. Gosh.

198
00:11:51,370 --> 00:11:55,150
Can't they give us a pass?
Maybe 30 more seconds.

199
00:11:55,150 --> 00:11:56,740
[He wanted more time with her
from the very beginning]

200
00:12:05,020 --> 00:12:06,550
What?

201
00:12:13,090 --> 00:12:17,500
- Is she crying?
- It must be sad. I think she'd cry, too.

202
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,610
Why...

203
00:12:23,130 --> 00:12:25,120
It's okay.

204
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:32,900
If I were more relaxed about it...

205
00:12:32,900 --> 00:12:36,100
I obviously have feelings for someone.

206
00:12:37,090 --> 00:12:42,200
I don't think
I'd feel comfortable dating you.

207
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:46,310
- Okay, okay.
- That was for Seong Min's sake, too.

208
00:12:47,690 --> 00:12:51,820
Why do I... Never mind.

209
00:12:51,820 --> 00:12:54,780
It must have been hard to bring it up.

210
00:12:54,780 --> 00:12:56,960
It's a difficult thing to say.

211
00:12:58,990 --> 00:13:03,830
Well, that's your true feeling.

212
00:13:03,830 --> 00:13:05,350
Yes.

213
00:13:07,260 --> 00:13:08,950
Got it.

214
00:13:10,330 --> 00:13:13,510
[She's afraid her constant
refusal hurt his feelings]

215
00:13:13,510 --> 00:13:15,860
You feel bad about stuff like that.

216
00:13:15,860 --> 00:13:19,390
Did you feel more impatient
than I did? Probably not.

217
00:13:21,610 --> 00:13:26,210
At first, I was just so aware of my feelings.

218
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:29,390
And I got to feel jealous, too.

219
00:13:30,400 --> 00:13:34,420
Why did you only take photos
with Wu Yeol on the boat?

220
00:13:36,190 --> 00:13:40,640
I felt emotions like that. I didn't
think I'd feel that way at 29.

221
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:42,300
[The more his feelings grew,]

222
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:47,800
[the more apparent things got]

223
00:13:47,800 --> 00:13:50,750
Don't... Don't avoid me so quickly.

224
00:13:50,750 --> 00:13:55,020
Why do you suddenly go cold?

225
00:13:55,020 --> 00:13:58,190
Why did you go cold
and turn your head like that?

226
00:13:58,190 --> 00:14:02,040
Right. Seong Min's feelings
grew a lot that day.

227
00:14:02,040 --> 00:14:04,420
There was the Beauty Digestive, too.

228
00:14:04,420 --> 00:14:07,700
- You're so...
- Hold on.

229
00:14:07,700 --> 00:14:10,180
[He got excited about small things]

230
00:14:22,380 --> 00:14:25,760
It'll be okay. It'll be okay. It's fine.

231
00:14:25,760 --> 00:14:29,520
I don't regret what happened at all.

232
00:14:31,630 --> 00:14:35,010
Don't cry. You are making me feel sad.

233
00:14:35,010 --> 00:14:36,660
You're making me feel sad. Don't cry.

234
00:14:36,660 --> 00:14:38,850
I don't want you to cry.

235
00:14:41,830 --> 00:14:46,790
You followed your heart. I think
that was the right thing to do.

236
00:14:49,620 --> 00:14:51,090
It's all good.

237
00:14:56,380 --> 00:14:57,390
It's all good.

238
00:14:57,390 --> 00:15:01,330
He looks more mature in front of Yu Gyeong.

239
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:12,100
Don't cry. You have to look pretty
for the next person.

240
00:15:15,620 --> 00:15:18,470
I think I'll only cry with you.

241
00:15:18,470 --> 00:15:20,440
Really?

242
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:22,440
Yay.

243
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:24,900
Seriously.

244
00:15:26,350 --> 00:15:27,260
[Meow]

245
00:15:27,900 --> 00:15:30,460
- There it is.
- Hi.

246
00:15:30,460 --> 00:15:33,450
- He kind of looks like you.
- He does?

247
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:38,210
[Unforgettable memories]

248
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:39,430
Sir.

249
00:15:39,430 --> 00:15:42,380
[What will they decide?]

250
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:48,310
[Happy]

251
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:52,800
[So Yun and Jun Hyeon's chat]

252
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:55,000
- You're here.
- I'm finally here.

253
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,750
Jun Hyeon looks different.

254
00:15:56,750 --> 00:16:00,780
- You look a little different today.
- Do I look okay?

255
00:16:00,780 --> 00:16:05,600
You surprised me. Ever since
I moved in, you look the most...

256
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:09,240
Really? I have never felt more tired.
But I haven't looked better.

257
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:11,660
I probably never looked uglier than now.

258
00:16:11,660 --> 00:16:14,810
- No, no.
- No?

259
00:16:14,810 --> 00:16:18,400
You can tell they feel
comfortable with each other.

260
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:22,690
I was most curious about our conversation.

261
00:16:22,690 --> 00:16:26,310
I think I had a deep connection with you.

262
00:16:27,290 --> 00:16:31,020
- I think ours was the deepest.
- I think so, too.

263
00:16:34,530 --> 00:16:38,390
Living here is hard in many ways.

264
00:16:39,650 --> 00:16:44,200
But since you were here...

265
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:47,860
I mean it. I'm being serious.

266
00:16:47,860 --> 00:16:53,010
I think it started being less
stressful at some point.

267
00:16:53,010 --> 00:16:56,380
That's what I thought was crazy, too.

268
00:16:56,380 --> 00:17:00,890
We didn't try to rely on each other.
It just happened naturally.

269
00:17:00,890 --> 00:17:03,760
Neither of us normally
relies on other people.

270
00:17:03,760 --> 00:17:09,130
We didn't even talk
about our stresses, either.

271
00:17:09,130 --> 00:17:12,370
To be honest, I didn't know
how stressed I was, either.

272
00:17:12,370 --> 00:17:16,870
My casual conversations and banter with you

273
00:17:16,870 --> 00:17:23,060
gave me so much strength each day.

274
00:17:23,060 --> 00:17:25,440
- What's wrong, So Yun?
- Huh?

275
00:17:25,440 --> 00:17:30,130
[He noticed her when she felt discouraged]

276
00:17:30,690 --> 00:17:32,430
I told Wu Yeol this.

277
00:17:32,430 --> 00:17:35,760
I would've seduced all four guys
if we had one more month.

278
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:38,980
Maybe not all four. Maybe one.

279
00:17:41,700 --> 00:17:45,960
Every time you talked to me,
you weren't just joking.

280
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:50,540
You noticed I was feeling discouraged

281
00:17:50,540 --> 00:17:54,920
and I was struggling to adjust.

282
00:17:54,920 --> 00:18:00,480
I could tell,
and I was really grateful for that.

283
00:18:01,470 --> 00:18:04,750
So, even when I was with everyone...

284
00:18:04,750 --> 00:18:07,390
Where's Jun Hyeon?

285
00:18:07,390 --> 00:18:09,840
I kept looking for you.

286
00:18:09,840 --> 00:18:13,010
Because I was relying on you unconsciously.

287
00:18:14,070 --> 00:18:17,000
Jun Hyeon? We're having
a girls' talk. Want to join us?

288
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:18,900
Yes.

289
00:18:18,900 --> 00:18:21,740
- I want this.
- No.

290
00:18:22,840 --> 00:18:24,780
Give me a blanket or something.

291
00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:26,540
I won't take it from you.

292
00:18:26,540 --> 00:18:28,650
It keeps going toward you.

293
00:18:28,650 --> 00:18:31,040
Gosh, seriously.

294
00:18:31,040 --> 00:18:32,120
[Which woman do you feel the
most comfortable with?]

295
00:18:32,120 --> 00:18:34,950
The person who makes me feel comfortable

296
00:18:34,950 --> 00:18:37,520
is probably So Yun.

297
00:18:38,350 --> 00:18:42,490
I think Jun Hyeon makes me
feel the most comfortable.

298
00:18:44,690 --> 00:18:47,700
I really relied on you a lot.

299
00:18:49,850 --> 00:18:55,210
That's a relief. I thought I was the
only one relying on you.

300
00:18:55,210 --> 00:18:57,930
They both had a very reassuring presence.

301
00:18:57,930 --> 00:19:00,180
They were the most honest, too.

302
00:19:01,970 --> 00:19:04,730
And you have a certain charm.

303
00:19:04,730 --> 00:19:07,500
You are more cheerful than you seem.

304
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:10,050
That's what I meant when I said,
"You can do it." You're bold.

305
00:19:10,050 --> 00:19:11,470
"You can do it."

306
00:19:11,470 --> 00:19:13,490
[The day they cooked together]

307
00:19:13,490 --> 00:19:17,120
- I knew you could do it.
- I can do it.

308
00:19:17,120 --> 00:19:19,000
Good job. You cooked.

309
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:22,650
She always gets things done.

310
00:19:22,650 --> 00:19:25,110
- I can do it.
- You sure can.

311
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:30,200
[That night]

312
00:19:30,200 --> 00:19:34,390
[Beluga of the Forest: You can do it]

313
00:19:35,900 --> 00:19:37,350
How moving.

314
00:19:37,350 --> 00:19:40,090
She is reminded of his charm.

315
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:42,690
In the end,

316
00:19:44,930 --> 00:19:53,330
I believe you'll make an honest
and admirable decision.

317
00:19:54,290 --> 00:19:57,310
Honest and admirable decision.

318
00:19:57,310 --> 00:20:01,340
You've been feeling a bit regretful lately.

319
00:20:03,010 --> 00:20:07,700
I believe you'll make a decision
you won't regret.

320
00:20:07,700 --> 00:20:10,890
You will be yourself in the end.

321
00:20:11,890 --> 00:20:14,920
Be honest, you know me.

322
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:16,670
What do I know?

323
00:20:16,670 --> 00:20:19,390
It's either Seo Won or you.

324
00:20:19,390 --> 00:20:22,330
The final choice is what matters.

325
00:20:23,390 --> 00:20:27,710
You'll praise me
whether I choose you or Seo Won.

326
00:20:27,710 --> 00:20:32,080
You're right. I just like you.

327
00:20:33,520 --> 00:20:36,100
I'm okay with everything you do.

328
00:20:36,100 --> 00:20:38,770
Gosh, seriously.

329
00:20:40,770 --> 00:20:43,190
He is so fond of her.

330
00:20:43,190 --> 00:20:44,730
Fighting.

331
00:20:47,090 --> 00:20:49,580
A relationship like that is a blessing.

332
00:20:49,580 --> 00:20:53,300
- I want a Blu-ray copy of this season.
- Really.

333
00:20:56,550 --> 00:20:59,320
[Min Ju and Seong Min's chat]

334
00:21:01,480 --> 00:21:04,200
- We meet again at this place.
- I know.

335
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:06,360
On these very seats.

336
00:21:07,090 --> 00:21:08,950
Wow...

337
00:21:08,950 --> 00:21:10,590
You're done talking, right?

338
00:21:10,590 --> 00:21:13,520
[They had a disconnect the
last time they were here]

339
00:21:14,370 --> 00:21:17,440
- This spot is a bit...
- That's why I'm not sitting here.

340
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:20,000
[They are sitting in the
adjacent seats this time]

341
00:21:31,180 --> 00:21:36,650
While adjusting to our lives here,

342
00:21:36,650 --> 00:21:40,270
we've been relying on each other a lot.

343
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:41,800
True.

344
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:48,490
It's been...

345
00:21:51,830 --> 00:21:53,750
so nice.

346
00:21:57,220 --> 00:22:01,660
We grew closer,
starting with the 10-minute talk.

347
00:22:02,550 --> 00:22:05,750
I was glad that we found it easy
to talk to each other.

348
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:10,640
When you walked toward me,
I thought we had something going on.

349
00:22:10,640 --> 00:22:14,770
Min Ju thought
they were meant to be from Day 1.

350
00:22:14,770 --> 00:22:18,180
- I want to light mine, too.
- Come here. Come here.

351
00:22:18,180 --> 00:22:22,530
I really loved the fact that there
was someone I was interested in.

352
00:22:22,530 --> 00:22:23,630
I know...

353
00:22:23,630 --> 00:22:27,320
Whenever I have dates with Seong Min,

354
00:22:27,320 --> 00:22:31,160
I reveal my feelings without realizing it.

355
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:33,730
[Who were you most concerned about today?]
I would say Seong Min for this, too.

356
00:22:34,540 --> 00:22:35,860
[Who brought you the most joy today?]

357
00:22:35,860 --> 00:22:37,930
This is Seong Min, too.

358
00:22:37,930 --> 00:22:41,310
I think this is also Seong Min.

359
00:22:41,310 --> 00:22:46,060
[He is the answer to every question]

360
00:22:46,060 --> 00:22:49,280
I've always been looking
for someone like that.

361
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:55,600
Someone on the same wavelength.

362
00:22:58,070 --> 00:23:00,040
No.

363
00:23:02,450 --> 00:23:05,110
[Who hurt you the most today?]

364
00:23:15,230 --> 00:23:18,680
That's the scariest part of liking someone.

365
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:20,440
That's right.

366
00:23:23,300 --> 00:23:24,820
Goodness.

367
00:23:34,280 --> 00:23:38,880
After having various chats with you,

368
00:23:38,880 --> 00:23:44,820
I was affected
by small comments or expressions.

369
00:23:44,820 --> 00:23:50,160
I think that led to an extreme situation.

370
00:23:50,160 --> 00:23:52,610
I find that to be a shame.

371
00:23:54,150 --> 00:23:58,870
If I hurt your feelings,
I apologize for that.

372
00:24:01,660 --> 00:24:03,820
You never did.

373
00:24:03,820 --> 00:24:09,270
You didn't have to try to talk to me
since your feelings were hurt.

374
00:24:09,270 --> 00:24:15,010
- I'm grateful that you made an effort.
- Yes, she really did.

375
00:24:15,010 --> 00:24:19,070
I'm really grateful.

376
00:24:20,110 --> 00:24:22,900
I'm unbelievably grateful.

377
00:24:22,900 --> 00:24:24,490
Me, too.

378
00:24:26,380 --> 00:24:30,230
We have feelings we exchanged.

379
00:24:30,230 --> 00:24:32,300
I think that...

380
00:24:32,300 --> 00:24:35,300
Thank you, Oppa. Did you prepare this?

381
00:24:35,300 --> 00:24:38,530
Thank you. I'm so moved.

382
00:24:44,650 --> 00:24:46,600
It's nice.

383
00:24:46,600 --> 00:24:52,030
I think you let me be myself

384
00:24:52,030 --> 00:24:56,280
and also made me be less of myself.

385
00:24:57,710 --> 00:25:01,150
I understand everything you say.

386
00:25:02,140 --> 00:25:04,140
All it takes is a facial expression.

387
00:25:04,140 --> 00:25:05,750
I know.

388
00:25:13,150 --> 00:25:15,310
So, I want you to...

389
00:25:17,760 --> 00:25:23,550
pursue your true feelings
without worrying about anything.

390
00:25:23,550 --> 00:25:25,700
Gosh, crazy.

391
00:25:25,700 --> 00:25:30,510
I want you to examine your heart honestly.

392
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:41,320
Let us make a decision we won't regret.

393
00:25:49,660 --> 00:25:53,390
[What kind of feelings are they left
with after this last chat?]

394
00:25:54,017 --> 00:25:54,899
What was that?

395
00:25:54,899 --> 00:25:58,100
That was another hurtful conversation today.

396
00:25:58,100 --> 00:25:59,720
I know. Her face...

397
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:04,960
Min Ju still tried to make Seong Min
feel comfortable until the end.

398
00:26:04,960 --> 00:26:06,690
- She tried so hard.
- That's right.

399
00:26:06,690 --> 00:26:10,460
Do you think she's still waiting
for him with her arms wide open?

400
00:26:10,460 --> 00:26:12,890
She was telling him that he could pursue her.

401
00:26:12,890 --> 00:26:16,340
She was half supportive and
half encouraging him.

402
00:26:16,340 --> 00:26:18,680
She's always been the same.

403
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:22,370
- She just seems to like his type.
- She's totally smitten.

404
00:26:22,370 --> 00:26:26,430
She'll have to understand
how Seong Min feels, too.

405
00:26:26,430 --> 00:26:30,510
Even if she knows he doesn't feel
for you, you can't just give up.

406
00:26:30,510 --> 00:26:33,360
It's hard to control your feelings.

407
00:26:36,740 --> 00:26:38,010
- Huh?
- Wu Yeol?

408
00:26:38,010 --> 00:26:40,030
Who are you?

409
00:26:41,030 --> 00:26:43,190
Oppa, why do you look so different today?

410
00:26:43,190 --> 00:26:45,120
What do you mean? I look the same.

411
00:26:46,120 --> 00:26:49,530
What? I've never seen that outfit.

412
00:26:49,530 --> 00:26:51,560
I got dolled up.

413
00:26:54,220 --> 00:26:56,430
How many people have you chatted with?

414
00:26:56,430 --> 00:26:58,310
It's a secret.

415
00:27:02,830 --> 00:27:04,660
He looks handsome.

416
00:27:08,250 --> 00:27:11,310
When we had a date then,

417
00:27:11,310 --> 00:27:16,850
we chose each other as
someone who changed us.

418
00:27:19,400 --> 00:27:22,070
When I waited for you at the park,

419
00:27:22,070 --> 00:27:25,030
I didn't think I would smile so brightly.

420
00:27:25,030 --> 00:27:29,470
I do that in front of you
without even realizing it.

421
00:27:29,470 --> 00:27:32,310
We smiled with you.

422
00:27:33,170 --> 00:27:36,760
I acted a bit bashful.

423
00:27:38,380 --> 00:27:41,630
Whenever I was with you,

424
00:27:42,590 --> 00:27:46,400
things felt very different.

425
00:27:46,400 --> 00:27:54,770
I think I've noticed a new side
of me with Jun Hyeon.

426
00:27:54,770 --> 00:27:57,080
Would you like this?

427
00:27:57,080 --> 00:27:58,680
Thank you.

428
00:27:59,570 --> 00:28:03,480
I wasn't the person I was familiar with.

429
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:08,770
The way he cares for people and his attitude

430
00:28:08,770 --> 00:28:13,360
made me realize I could be treated like that.

431
00:28:13,360 --> 00:28:15,880
That was new to me.

432
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:17,860
Jun Hyeon is the best.

433
00:28:17,860 --> 00:28:22,450
It made me feel cautious.

434
00:28:22,450 --> 00:28:25,200
But in a positive way.

435
00:28:25,200 --> 00:28:31,800
I think it's Jun Hyeon for that reason.

436
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:35,110
I saw a totally new side of me.

437
00:28:35,110 --> 00:28:37,050
It was so nice.

438
00:28:38,470 --> 00:28:41,070
I am grateful for you in so many ways.

439
00:28:42,090 --> 00:28:43,780
I'm glad.

440
00:28:46,060 --> 00:28:48,290
Looks like she's about to cry.

441
00:28:50,680 --> 00:28:57,230
I realize you've been so considerate of me.

442
00:28:57,230 --> 00:28:59,800
- Am I wrong?
- I have.

443
00:28:59,800 --> 00:29:02,180
I overdid it.

444
00:29:02,180 --> 00:29:04,630
- I did it too much.
- Really?

445
00:29:04,630 --> 00:29:08,530
So, I thought...

446
00:29:08,530 --> 00:29:14,790
every little considerate gesture of yours

447
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:19,460
was very moving.

448
00:29:19,460 --> 00:29:22,540
Jun Hyeon is like that to everyone.

449
00:29:22,540 --> 00:29:28,700
I learned that
you can love someone at that pace.

450
00:29:30,960 --> 00:29:32,700
The letter...

451
00:29:33,830 --> 00:29:37,030
I knew it was yours immediately.

452
00:29:37,030 --> 00:29:39,520
He needs to talk about that now.

453
00:29:42,370 --> 00:29:44,820
[He recognized
Yu Gyeong's letter immediately]

454
00:29:46,620 --> 00:29:49,420
I knew you would know.

455
00:29:51,140 --> 00:29:53,800
I knew it was you right away.

456
00:29:55,870 --> 00:29:57,760
When I was on the date,

457
00:30:00,160 --> 00:30:03,140
I thought about you a bit.

458
00:30:09,040 --> 00:30:16,450
I think I enjoyed my time with you
the most while I was here.

459
00:30:18,330 --> 00:30:23,960
To be honest, I expected the least from you.

460
00:30:23,960 --> 00:30:26,170
Regardless of my feelings.

461
00:30:27,240 --> 00:30:28,820
But...

462
00:30:30,390 --> 00:30:35,070
the more I saw you,

463
00:30:35,070 --> 00:30:38,420
the more I realized
that you were a good person.

464
00:30:40,170 --> 00:30:44,440
I wondered why other people hurt you.

465
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:46,850
- Really?
- Right.

466
00:30:46,850 --> 00:30:50,560
I wondered why they didn't understand you.

467
00:30:50,560 --> 00:30:53,230
I thought a lot while reading your letter.

468
00:30:54,230 --> 00:30:57,360
It's nice that he thought that
while reading her letter.

469
00:30:57,360 --> 00:31:00,360
He's good at reading her thoughts.

470
00:31:00,360 --> 00:31:04,600
I liked what you wrote.

471
00:31:04,600 --> 00:31:10,420
You've been hurt,
but you won't be afraid of it.

472
00:31:10,420 --> 00:31:13,340
You'll do anything for someone you trust.

473
00:31:13,340 --> 00:31:15,600
He remembers everything.

474
00:31:15,600 --> 00:31:22,640
If they trust me, I'm willing to do anything.

475
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:29,870
That's why I always choose
that path despite my fear.

476
00:31:29,870 --> 00:31:33,620
I thought that was so cool. If you...

477
00:31:35,050 --> 00:31:42,430
live that way, someone who's truly amazing

478
00:31:45,690 --> 00:31:48,930
will recognize you.

479
00:31:51,600 --> 00:31:59,340
There are still many good people
who can recognize that.

480
00:31:59,340 --> 00:32:03,920
There must be many people
like that around you.

481
00:32:06,220 --> 00:32:08,450
He's making me tear up.

482
00:32:08,450 --> 00:32:13,730
I hope you don't get your
heart broken a lot in the future.

483
00:32:13,730 --> 00:32:15,970
This is even sadder.

484
00:32:17,160 --> 00:32:19,060
I don't want to let anyone go.

485
00:32:19,060 --> 00:32:21,060
[His sincere last goodbye]

486
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:24,270
[Feeling moved]

487
00:32:24,270 --> 00:32:27,200
Jun Hyeon's last confession was so him.

488
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:32,550
Of all the love confessions
he's given in his life,

489
00:32:32,550 --> 00:32:35,050
this must have taken the most courage.

490
00:32:35,050 --> 00:32:37,460
"I thought of you while on
a date with someone else."

491
00:32:37,460 --> 00:32:38,980
- That was nice.
- I like you the most.

492
00:32:38,980 --> 00:32:41,560
But it didn't feel demanding at all.

493
00:32:41,560 --> 00:32:43,600
- Not at all.
- It felt so kind.

494
00:32:43,600 --> 00:32:48,760
I thought her tears meant that
she was feeling healed.

495
00:32:48,760 --> 00:32:50,670
That's right.

496
00:32:53,600 --> 00:32:57,020
- Wu Yeol.
- His bangs are down like in the beginning.

497
00:32:57,020 --> 00:32:59,920
I haven't seen you like this in a while.

498
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:01,270
I covered my forehead today.

499
00:33:01,270 --> 00:33:02,860
[Staring]

500
00:33:03,450 --> 00:33:04,990
You like it?

501
00:33:06,250 --> 00:33:08,200
It suits you.

502
00:33:13,400 --> 00:33:15,550
You're barefoot.

503
00:33:15,550 --> 00:33:17,460
There were no slippers.

504
00:33:20,140 --> 00:33:21,780
Have you eaten?

505
00:33:23,310 --> 00:33:26,900
- I had salt bread.
- So cute.

506
00:33:26,900 --> 00:33:29,370
I had salt bread today.

507
00:33:29,370 --> 00:33:31,330
[Flustered]

508
00:33:31,330 --> 00:33:33,590
[Yellow's first provocation]

509
00:33:36,380 --> 00:33:38,060
Why did you eat my nickname?

510
00:33:38,060 --> 00:33:39,300
[Laughing]

511
00:33:39,300 --> 00:33:41,700
Is that your nickname?

512
00:33:41,700 --> 00:33:43,300
[Oops]

513
00:33:43,300 --> 00:33:46,380
[Acting ignorant]

514
00:33:46,380 --> 00:33:48,620
I had salt bread today.

515
00:33:48,620 --> 00:33:49,960
[Pausing]

516
00:33:51,760 --> 00:33:54,130
[She got him again]

517
00:33:54,860 --> 00:33:56,650
Stop eating it.

518
00:34:04,374 --> 00:34:08,120
I think we spent
the most time together, right?

519
00:34:08,120 --> 00:34:09,400
Is that so?

520
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:13,170
- We had the most dates together, too.
- Right.

521
00:34:13,170 --> 00:34:15,650
Today is Sunday.

522
00:34:15,650 --> 00:34:18,880
- We're a Sunday couple, you know.
- True.

523
00:34:25,550 --> 00:34:28,700
It's finally hitting me.

524
00:34:31,290 --> 00:34:34,330
This is our last conversation here.

525
00:34:35,230 --> 00:34:37,190
I thought it was really nice.

526
00:34:43,780 --> 00:34:48,250
For almost a month,

527
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:56,000
you changed me the most.

528
00:34:58,670 --> 00:35:01,300
- Really?
- That's true.

529
00:35:01,300 --> 00:35:04,040
- So...
- Wu Yeol changed a lot.

530
00:35:04,040 --> 00:35:05,970
- Totally.
- In a good way.

531
00:35:05,970 --> 00:35:08,670
I only have good memories.

532
00:35:16,790 --> 00:35:20,130
How do you feel when you are with me?

533
00:35:20,130 --> 00:35:21,830
- Me?
- Yes.

534
00:35:22,690 --> 00:35:25,140
I think it feels natural.

535
00:35:25,140 --> 00:35:28,160
- Really?
- Yes, why?

536
00:35:30,100 --> 00:35:35,040
You said that was important to you.

537
00:35:35,040 --> 00:35:38,170
I was curious how you felt.

538
00:35:39,070 --> 00:35:41,210
I think it feels natural.

539
00:35:44,370 --> 00:35:49,000
I feel the most comfortable.

540
00:35:56,300 --> 00:36:02,110
I don't usually rely on people
or ask for help.

541
00:36:02,110 --> 00:36:05,960
I always thought
I should give anything a try.

542
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:07,920
I wanted to become tough.

543
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:11,300
So, I moved to Seoul without a plan.

544
00:36:11,300 --> 00:36:14,100
I had expenses while living alone.

545
00:36:14,100 --> 00:36:16,980
I had some money saved.

546
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:23,230
Using the time deposit,
I paid my security deposit.

547
00:36:23,230 --> 00:36:26,450
I thought I had to make money
while I was young.

548
00:36:26,450 --> 00:36:29,720
So, I worked seven days a week.

549
00:36:29,720 --> 00:36:37,800
And I didn't want to call up
my parents for their help.

550
00:36:38,910 --> 00:36:44,260
I thought I was okay while living alone.

551
00:36:44,260 --> 00:36:48,640
But I guess I have felt lonely.

552
00:36:50,180 --> 00:36:53,250
I've felt like talking to someone.

553
00:36:54,510 --> 00:37:02,250
Before I came here, I thought
I could overcome things alone.

554
00:37:02,250 --> 00:37:05,440
I've been thinking that, but...

555
00:37:08,670 --> 00:37:11,950
I think I've been suppressing those feelings.

556
00:37:11,950 --> 00:37:15,690
- It's fun to walk.
- Is it fun?

557
00:37:15,690 --> 00:37:17,230
So fun.

558
00:37:17,230 --> 00:37:18,230
[Twirling]

559
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,440
I'm not doing it.

560
00:37:21,270 --> 00:37:24,070
You have to know when to spend.

561
00:37:24,070 --> 00:37:27,030
- Let everyone see them.
- Like this?

562
00:37:27,030 --> 00:37:29,860
[He missed out on fun
since he grew up quickly]

563
00:37:29,860 --> 00:37:33,500
After I moved into Signal House...

564
00:37:33,500 --> 00:37:36,490
[Wu Yeol's world started changing]

565
00:37:36,490 --> 00:37:37,620
Are you having breakfast?

566
00:37:37,620 --> 00:37:46,840
I realized I've been missing these things.

567
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:49,900
[Smiling]

568
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:53,100
- What should I have for lunch?
- Food.

569
00:37:53,100 --> 00:37:57,030
I think Yu Gyeong makes me laugh.

570
00:38:01,280 --> 00:38:05,690
She's so cute in a pure, uncorrupted way.

571
00:38:06,700 --> 00:38:08,780
That side of her...

572
00:38:08,780 --> 00:38:11,950
[The pure person who makes him laugh]

573
00:38:14,650 --> 00:38:18,720
made me smile and imagine a happy scenario.

574
00:38:18,720 --> 00:38:21,370
Someone the same inside and out.

575
00:38:23,540 --> 00:38:26,160
I feel like my true self.

576
00:38:29,180 --> 00:38:31,450
Your true self.

577
00:38:33,570 --> 00:38:34,620
[Satisfied]

578
00:38:34,620 --> 00:38:38,620
A man who changed because
of her. How nice is that?

579
00:38:38,620 --> 00:38:40,150
Thank you.

580
00:38:42,550 --> 00:38:44,840
Why can't I look you in the eye?

581
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:46,440
Thank you.

582
00:38:52,100 --> 00:38:53,740
As for me...

583
00:38:54,740 --> 00:38:59,550
I think you let me...

584
00:38:59,550 --> 00:39:02,890
feel the most emotions.

585
00:39:03,940 --> 00:39:06,150
That's very significant.

586
00:39:06,150 --> 00:39:08,410
Thank you.

587
00:39:10,900 --> 00:39:14,310
I'm so mad at you.

588
00:39:14,310 --> 00:39:15,670
[Hehe]

589
00:39:15,670 --> 00:39:18,150
That's because she likes him.

590
00:39:19,720 --> 00:39:22,540
I have the most fun when I'm with you.

591
00:39:22,540 --> 00:39:24,270
I feel the same.

592
00:39:26,020 --> 00:39:28,700
I'm the happiest when I'm with you.

593
00:39:29,950 --> 00:39:32,010
There's something I want to say.

594
00:39:34,260 --> 00:39:37,030
[What is it? What is it!]

595
00:39:38,660 --> 00:39:43,280
I don't think this is the end.

596
00:39:45,370 --> 00:39:47,070
Or is it?

597
00:39:50,230 --> 00:39:52,070
Are you sure?

598
00:39:57,060 --> 00:39:59,970
I hope I get a chance to tell you.

599
00:40:03,740 --> 00:40:06,840
[Will his true feelings be reciprocated?]

600
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:09,790
There hasn't been such an eventful couple.

601
00:40:09,790 --> 00:40:13,750
You can say she changed someone she likes.

602
00:40:13,750 --> 00:40:16,030
That's a great love.

603
00:40:16,030 --> 00:40:20,120
She is young, but I think we're
learning a lot from her.

604
00:40:20,120 --> 00:40:21,130
Totally.

605
00:40:21,130 --> 00:40:24,440
It's love when you feel many emotions.

606
00:40:24,440 --> 00:40:26,720
You feel angry and stressed.

607
00:40:26,720 --> 00:40:29,480
You feel hurt, at peace, sad, and tearful.

608
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:33,380
You feel all that with your first love.

609
00:40:33,380 --> 00:40:35,810
I feel like they are both
going through that a lot.

610
00:40:35,810 --> 00:40:39,090
If they end up with a happy ending,

611
00:40:39,090 --> 00:40:42,260
I'll feel so happy.

612
00:40:42,260 --> 00:40:46,630
- The world will suddenly feel brighter.
- I know.

613
00:40:52,630 --> 00:40:54,500
Who's this?

614
00:40:54,500 --> 00:40:58,260
- Seo Won.
- I feel for this couple.

615
00:40:58,260 --> 00:41:00,290
You dressed nicely.

616
00:41:00,290 --> 00:41:02,130
It's the last day.

617
00:41:03,120 --> 00:41:04,750
I'm so nervous. It's like the first day.

618
00:41:04,750 --> 00:41:07,390
It's so cute that he wore
a suit for the last day.

619
00:41:07,390 --> 00:41:10,820
First day? How is your
first impression of me today?

620
00:41:11,640 --> 00:41:13,830
You're like a pure rabbit.

621
00:41:15,290 --> 00:41:16,850
[Sigh]

622
00:41:16,850 --> 00:41:19,520
- Seriously.
- What, what?

623
00:41:19,520 --> 00:41:21,660
Why are you sighing?

624
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:30,100
I have so many things to say.

625
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:32,240
But I feel like I can't say anything.

626
00:41:32,240 --> 00:41:35,280
It's okay. You can do it.

627
00:41:45,190 --> 00:41:50,600
When do you think
I developed feelings for you?

628
00:41:54,330 --> 00:41:56,950
During our first date?

629
00:42:00,050 --> 00:42:02,690
- Even before that.
- What?

630
00:42:03,640 --> 00:42:08,230
You were making ramen after work.

631
00:42:08,230 --> 00:42:10,570
When we made eye contact then,

632
00:42:10,570 --> 00:42:14,630
I was like, "Was he always this handsome?"

633
00:42:16,990 --> 00:42:19,220
What are you saying?

634
00:42:20,910 --> 00:42:24,520
And then when we all talked together,

635
00:42:24,520 --> 00:42:26,560
different sides of you were revealed.

636
00:42:26,560 --> 00:42:29,650
Some people can't say "I love you" easily.

637
00:42:29,650 --> 00:42:31,860
I say it every day.

638
00:42:31,860 --> 00:42:34,880
Don't you feel hurt when
they stop the cutesy talk?

639
00:42:34,880 --> 00:42:37,280
- "Okay, babe."
- After a fight?

640
00:42:37,280 --> 00:42:39,680
When they're like,
"Good night," I can't sleep.

641
00:42:39,680 --> 00:42:41,370
[She was drawn to his cheerful side]

642
00:42:41,370 --> 00:42:45,590
It's observant of her
to notice that side of him.

643
00:42:45,590 --> 00:42:50,150
When I realized how I felt,

644
00:42:50,150 --> 00:42:52,790
I thought it was a bit too late.

645
00:42:55,600 --> 00:43:02,400
The fact that he has feelings
for someone else

646
00:43:03,290 --> 00:43:09,140
is becoming clear. That's my biggest fear.

647
00:43:10,430 --> 00:43:14,550
I know where your heart is headed.

648
00:43:16,620 --> 00:43:19,640
So, I didn't want to pressure you.

649
00:43:19,640 --> 00:43:21,220
If I...

650
00:43:23,780 --> 00:43:27,820
let things go without saying anything...

651
00:43:27,820 --> 00:43:31,190
If we made a final decision and things ended,

652
00:43:32,130 --> 00:43:36,130
I thought everything would be okay.

653
00:43:36,130 --> 00:43:39,090
I wanted you to...

654
00:43:39,090 --> 00:43:44,940
spend the rest of the time with
the person you want more than me.

655
00:43:44,940 --> 00:43:46,790
Because...

656
00:43:50,840 --> 00:43:54,880
Because that would make you happier.

657
00:43:54,880 --> 00:43:58,700
My gosh. So Yun's heartbreaking love story.

658
00:43:59,670 --> 00:44:05,090
Wow. All the puzzle pieces are
coming together after hearing you.

659
00:44:05,090 --> 00:44:08,490
I feel like I understand what he means.

660
00:44:08,490 --> 00:44:11,410
But then...

661
00:44:11,410 --> 00:44:16,030
I felt so much regret today.

662
00:44:18,820 --> 00:44:23,330
- I wish I were a little bit more selfish.
- You should've.

663
00:44:23,330 --> 00:44:25,850
I got goofy with you for no reason.

664
00:44:25,850 --> 00:44:28,970
Come on. Come on.

665
00:44:28,970 --> 00:44:32,680
- And I kept teasing you, too.
- Let it sit for 5 to 10 minutes.

666
00:44:32,680 --> 00:44:34,350
Sit down. Sit down.

667
00:44:34,350 --> 00:44:36,020
[Staring]

668
00:44:36,020 --> 00:44:37,670
What?

669
00:44:37,670 --> 00:44:40,950
Don't look at me. Sorry, sorry.

670
00:44:40,950 --> 00:44:47,280
I noticed myself being more
affected by everything you say.

671
00:44:49,770 --> 00:44:52,790
So, I wanted to admit my feelings

672
00:44:53,860 --> 00:44:58,050
and ask you everything.

673
00:44:58,050 --> 00:44:59,700
I was...

674
00:45:02,260 --> 00:45:09,070
curious if you just thought
of me as a close friend.

675
00:45:18,250 --> 00:45:19,710
Gosh.

676
00:45:23,380 --> 00:45:28,440
When I was asked to name two
women I'm most interested in,

677
00:45:31,300 --> 00:45:33,490
I always mentioned your name.

678
00:45:40,240 --> 00:45:43,030
And actually,
in the early morning two days ago,

679
00:45:44,990 --> 00:45:47,120
I read the letters I got.

680
00:45:51,400 --> 00:45:54,360
I cried the most while reading yours.

681
00:45:54,360 --> 00:45:56,190
He cried then.

682
00:45:56,190 --> 00:46:01,450
I'm worried if they would accept me as I am

683
00:46:01,450 --> 00:46:07,480
and still like me. That's my biggest fear.

684
00:46:08,600 --> 00:46:11,090
- I was like that, too.
- I can't watch this.

685
00:46:11,090 --> 00:46:12,910
[It affected Seo Won's heart deeply]

686
00:46:12,910 --> 00:46:16,210
Gosh, Seo Won turned red.

687
00:46:16,980 --> 00:46:18,520
Just by...

688
00:46:21,490 --> 00:46:23,610
reading your letter...

689
00:46:26,110 --> 00:46:28,620
I could see how afraid you are.

690
00:46:33,210 --> 00:46:38,440
I like to show myself as I am.

691
00:46:40,090 --> 00:46:46,600
But I thought that could end up
stressing you out more.

692
00:46:53,350 --> 00:46:54,690
[Choking up]

693
00:47:04,220 --> 00:47:07,050
[Trying to hold it in]

694
00:47:11,430 --> 00:47:13,900
My gosh.

695
00:47:17,100 --> 00:47:18,860
I...

696
00:47:21,430 --> 00:47:24,630
discovered my feelings much later.

697
00:47:25,870 --> 00:47:28,930
But if saying this to you

698
00:47:32,060 --> 00:47:34,130
made things awkward between us

699
00:47:34,130 --> 00:47:39,080
or if you stopped joking around with me,

700
00:47:39,080 --> 00:47:41,450
I'd really hate that.

701
00:47:47,460 --> 00:47:51,890
I kept displaying my true feelings as a joke.

702
00:47:58,030 --> 00:48:00,230
Once we leave this place,

703
00:48:04,310 --> 00:48:07,140
the feelings I have for you

704
00:48:08,060 --> 00:48:11,370
would be my burden to carry.

705
00:48:20,500 --> 00:48:26,330
I hope my telling you this today

706
00:48:28,740 --> 00:48:35,160
doesn't ruin our old relationship.

707
00:48:35,160 --> 00:48:40,870
I want you to keep teasing, surprising me,

708
00:48:41,720 --> 00:48:45,430
and make jokes with me.

709
00:48:45,430 --> 00:48:47,590
We can play games together, too.

710
00:48:50,470 --> 00:48:52,200
I will.

711
00:48:59,590 --> 00:49:02,640
[Finally expressing her true feelings]

712
00:49:07,530 --> 00:49:10,120
- I'm sorry.
- You did the right thing.

713
00:49:13,400 --> 00:49:17,200
I feel so flustered, too.

714
00:49:17,200 --> 00:49:21,710
Everything about you must have
had a big impact on me.

715
00:49:25,230 --> 00:49:30,030
[When did the feelings grow so much?]

716
00:49:36,730 --> 00:49:40,630
You can't help your feelings for someone.

717
00:49:46,090 --> 00:49:49,540
I have always acted cheerful, but...

718
00:49:51,390 --> 00:49:53,580
Why are they crying so much?

719
00:49:53,580 --> 00:49:57,180
But since you're so honest with me,

720
00:49:57,180 --> 00:50:01,170
I'm back to my honest self, too.

721
00:50:06,710 --> 00:50:14,510
You told me I'm the real deal
out of the eight.

722
00:50:14,510 --> 00:50:17,470
But I wanted to tell you the same.

723
00:50:24,290 --> 00:50:25,910
Thank you.

724
00:50:36,460 --> 00:50:39,330
Tsuki, hand me a tissue.

725
00:50:40,170 --> 00:50:43,720
Looks like Seo Won was affected by that.

726
00:50:44,860 --> 00:50:52,320
We cried like babies just now,

727
00:50:52,320 --> 00:50:57,120
but once we leave this place,

728
00:50:58,770 --> 00:51:02,700
we'll go back to our normal selves.

729
00:51:02,700 --> 00:51:04,460
Why? You never know.

730
00:51:04,460 --> 00:51:06,160
I promise.

731
00:51:08,620 --> 00:51:10,340
I promise.

732
00:51:12,650 --> 00:51:14,300
Thank you.

733
00:51:15,250 --> 00:51:20,090
You are unpredictable until the end.

734
00:51:20,090 --> 00:51:25,030
You're so amazing in a good way.

735
00:51:25,030 --> 00:51:27,190
Do as you like, Noona.

736
00:51:27,190 --> 00:51:29,580
You won't be able to handle it.

737
00:51:30,750 --> 00:51:32,970
Let me breathe, please.

738
00:51:36,680 --> 00:51:39,680
Why are we crying and laughing?

739
00:51:42,560 --> 00:51:43,740
Please, I beg you.

740
00:51:43,740 --> 00:51:47,100
- Seo Won and So Yun are good people.
- It's hard to be that good.

741
00:51:47,100 --> 00:51:49,340
Let's go to an internet cafe after this.

742
00:51:49,340 --> 00:51:54,130
We'd better. I'll visit you in Sinsa often.

743
00:51:54,130 --> 00:51:55,730
Feel free to come.

744
00:51:56,820 --> 00:51:58,310
Please.

745
00:52:00,620 --> 00:52:02,170
Leave.

746
00:52:02,170 --> 00:52:03,550
Okay.

747
00:52:04,810 --> 00:52:07,070
I'm really leaving.

748
00:52:07,070 --> 00:52:08,680
Don't go.

749
00:52:09,800 --> 00:52:12,110
He's falling apart.

750
00:52:13,720 --> 00:52:16,720
Seriously. I'll call the police on you.

751
00:52:16,720 --> 00:52:19,460
This is so So Yun.

752
00:52:19,460 --> 00:52:22,590
You're driving me crazy. I'll go, Noona.

753
00:52:22,590 --> 00:52:24,540
See you again.

754
00:52:24,540 --> 00:52:26,730
See you again.

755
00:52:26,730 --> 00:52:28,510
Bye.

756
00:52:28,510 --> 00:52:32,190
[Leaving after crying and
laughing for 45 minutes]

757
00:52:32,190 --> 00:52:34,090
They chatted for 45 minutes?

758
00:52:34,090 --> 00:52:37,000
They talked the longest.

759
00:52:37,960 --> 00:52:40,730
[So Yun expressed her feelings one last time]

760
00:52:40,730 --> 00:52:43,890
[And Seo Won's feelings exploded]

761
00:52:43,890 --> 00:52:45,930
Oh, no...

762
00:52:48,970 --> 00:52:55,460
[His feelings grew out of control]

763
00:52:57,390 --> 00:53:01,400
I'm learning a lot this season.

764
00:53:01,400 --> 00:53:03,610
They were given 10 minutes,

765
00:53:03,610 --> 00:53:05,920
but they chatted for 45 minutes.

766
00:53:05,920 --> 00:53:10,850
She said she wanted him to spend
time with the person he likes.

767
00:53:10,850 --> 00:53:13,350
That's why she wasn't proactive.

768
00:53:13,350 --> 00:53:18,190
And then Seo Won said hearing that
made the puzzle pieces come together.

769
00:53:18,190 --> 00:53:21,850
He must have started crying, thinking,
"That's how she's been feeling."

770
00:53:21,850 --> 00:53:27,440
I also think their relationship could
easily grow in the long run.

771
00:53:27,440 --> 00:53:29,930
- But what about today?
- Today actually...

772
00:53:29,930 --> 00:53:32,190
They won't choose each other at this stage?

773
00:53:32,190 --> 00:53:34,950
I think So Yun will choose Seo Won.

774
00:53:34,950 --> 00:53:38,900
But as of now, honestly speaking,
Seo Won probably won't...

775
00:53:38,900 --> 00:53:46,250
But I'm not sure how his
feelings will change later.

776
00:53:46,250 --> 00:53:48,740
I haven't been to the rooftop since then.

777
00:53:48,740 --> 00:53:52,260
- I went up often.
- Why?

778
00:53:52,260 --> 00:53:54,840
- It's the last sunset.
- So moving.

779
00:53:54,840 --> 00:53:55,950
So pretty.

780
00:53:55,950 --> 00:53:58,560
The sunset must have been
so pretty in person.

781
00:53:58,560 --> 00:54:02,260
- The sun happens to be setting now.
- Perfect timing.

782
00:54:02,260 --> 00:54:04,930
- They must feel so emotional.
- I know.

783
00:54:05,730 --> 00:54:08,080
I want to take the same photo again.

784
00:54:08,080 --> 00:54:09,570
That was Day 4.

785
00:54:09,570 --> 00:54:13,120
- It was snowing so much back then.
- I'll take one from above.

786
00:54:13,120 --> 00:54:16,390
They talked formally to each other.

787
00:54:16,390 --> 00:54:18,690
We were young then.

788
00:54:25,820 --> 00:54:27,270
[They grew closer, but things
got more complicated]

789
00:54:27,270 --> 00:54:28,890
They must be tearing up.

790
00:54:28,890 --> 00:54:31,960
- I think I would.
- Seriously.

791
00:54:32,990 --> 00:54:34,390
[Unsettling]

792
00:54:36,760 --> 00:54:39,400
Jun Hyeon can tell Yu Gyeong
is having a hard time.

793
00:54:39,400 --> 00:54:41,120
Come here, Yu Gyeong.

794
00:54:41,120 --> 00:54:42,930
My voice cracked.

795
00:54:42,930 --> 00:54:44,760
Let's say "fighting" three times.

796
00:54:44,760 --> 00:54:47,520
- One, two, three. Fighting!
- Fighting!

797
00:54:47,520 --> 00:54:50,860
[These two had a lot of concerns
before the final decision]

798
00:54:50,860 --> 00:54:52,710
We'll take one of you guys first.

799
00:54:52,710 --> 00:54:54,100
What's that?

800
00:54:54,100 --> 00:54:57,600
Your hands are visible. This is good.

801
00:54:57,600 --> 00:54:59,670
That's your signature pose.

802
00:55:02,160 --> 00:55:04,180
You found your signature pose.

803
00:55:04,180 --> 00:55:06,010
[Seo Won remembered So Yun's habit]

804
00:55:06,010 --> 00:55:08,210
How is he so attentive?

805
00:55:08,210 --> 00:55:11,790
- Seo Won is such a good kid.
- He's a good person.

806
00:55:11,790 --> 00:55:17,990
[So Yun's habit was recorded
on Seo Won's phone]

807
00:55:17,990 --> 00:55:20,500
I'll take one now.

808
00:55:20,500 --> 00:55:23,100
Ta-da!

809
00:55:23,990 --> 00:55:26,900
Smile. Smile a bit.

810
00:55:27,780 --> 00:55:29,010
[Smiling]

811
00:55:29,010 --> 00:55:30,140
Nice.

812
00:55:30,140 --> 00:55:31,220
What should we do?

813
00:55:31,220 --> 00:55:34,080
- Do something manly?
- Same pose?

814
00:55:34,080 --> 00:55:35,900
- That's nice.
- I know.

815
00:55:35,900 --> 00:55:38,200
They look so nice together.

816
00:55:38,200 --> 00:55:41,590
- Why are you locking arms?
- We should do it, too.

817
00:55:41,590 --> 00:55:43,060
One, two, three.

818
00:55:43,060 --> 00:55:44,570
[Holding tightly]

819
00:55:47,770 --> 00:55:49,820
Nice.

820
00:55:49,820 --> 00:55:51,640
So pretty.

821
00:55:52,700 --> 00:55:55,150
Should we take a group shot now?

822
00:55:57,500 --> 00:56:00,670
- Come closer.
- "Come closer."

823
00:56:02,190 --> 00:56:03,650
[Checking]

824
00:56:03,650 --> 00:56:06,490
- Jun Hyeon was next to him.
- Come to the center.

825
00:56:06,490 --> 00:56:08,870
She must be aware of him.

826
00:56:10,510 --> 00:56:14,340
- It's good here.
- I told you the sunset is pretty.

827
00:56:14,340 --> 00:56:16,320
Come here.

828
00:56:17,740 --> 00:56:20,670
[A month in the Signal House]

829
00:56:20,670 --> 00:56:25,050
[How will they remember it?]

830
00:56:25,050 --> 00:56:28,080
This will be a beautiful memory.

831
00:56:34,600 --> 00:56:36,300
Come here for a second.

832
00:56:36,300 --> 00:56:37,560
Wait here.

833
00:56:37,560 --> 00:56:40,860
- Why does he want her to sit down?
- What is it?

834
00:56:44,020 --> 00:56:45,050
Here it is.

835
00:56:45,050 --> 00:56:46,680
[Rummaging]

836
00:56:46,680 --> 00:56:48,530
What, what, what?

837
00:56:55,430 --> 00:56:58,540
[Wu Yeol gives her a letter]

838
00:56:58,540 --> 00:57:00,620
- He wrote her a letter.
- Good job.

839
00:57:00,620 --> 00:57:02,530
That's great.

840
00:57:04,020 --> 00:57:05,340
[Yu Gyeong is reading the letter quietly]

841
00:57:05,340 --> 00:57:08,000
- He did something so sweet.
- I know.

842
00:57:08,000 --> 00:57:11,810
- Men do that once they've been changed.
- True.

843
00:57:11,810 --> 00:57:13,450
[He received a letter
from Yu Gyeong two days ago]

844
00:57:13,450 --> 00:57:16,950
She doesn't create a distance like me.

845
00:57:16,950 --> 00:57:19,470
She's honest with her feelings.

846
00:57:19,470 --> 00:57:24,820
Yu Gyeong has the courage
to be devoted to someone.

847
00:57:27,400 --> 00:57:37,500
[Wu Yeol's sincere feelings for Yu Gyeong]

848
00:57:37,500 --> 00:57:43,190
You're the only one
who entertains me like this.

849
00:57:43,190 --> 00:57:44,990
Really?

850
00:57:48,570 --> 00:57:50,690
Do you have the most fun
when you are with me?

851
00:57:50,690 --> 00:57:53,020
Yes, and I like it.

852
00:57:53,020 --> 00:57:55,520
- I like feeling that way.
- Really?

853
00:57:55,520 --> 00:57:59,360
I am so curious about this.
Do you get jealous?

854
00:57:59,360 --> 00:58:00,810
- Me?
- Yes.

855
00:58:00,810 --> 00:58:03,420
I thought I didn't.

856
00:58:03,420 --> 00:58:07,530
- But I do when I really like someone.
- Really?

857
00:58:07,530 --> 00:58:08,529
Cute dog.

858
00:58:08,529 --> 00:58:11,270
Hold on, what's this?
There's something here.

859
00:58:11,270 --> 00:58:16,370
[Busy Hamster's postcard
was in Yu Gyeong's book]

860
00:58:18,200 --> 00:58:20,210
[Shaking]

861
00:58:20,210 --> 00:58:21,700
Hamster...

862
00:58:21,700 --> 00:58:24,620
Did you say that out of jealousy?

863
00:58:24,620 --> 00:58:28,400
- Yes, I wouldn't say it otherwise.
- Really?

864
00:58:28,400 --> 00:58:36,700
[At some point]

865
00:58:36,700 --> 00:58:40,140
[He started lingering around her]

866
00:58:40,140 --> 00:58:45,300
[Without even realizing]

867
00:58:45,300 --> 00:58:52,140
[He started feeling bothered]

868
00:58:52,140 --> 00:58:53,960
Are you an INFP?

869
00:58:54,920 --> 00:58:56,380
No, I'm an ISFP.

870
00:58:56,380 --> 00:59:00,420
I'm sometimes an ISFP.
I switch between the two.

871
00:59:00,420 --> 00:59:05,480
[Feeling jealous for the first time]

872
00:59:05,480 --> 00:59:08,490
I think I get jealous all the time.

873
00:59:09,320 --> 00:59:11,160
You do?

874
00:59:11,160 --> 00:59:12,780
That's cute.

875
00:59:12,780 --> 00:59:15,180
Is being jealous cute?

876
00:59:15,180 --> 00:59:17,470
It is. It means you like someone that much.

877
00:59:17,470 --> 00:59:18,930
Geez.

878
00:59:19,730 --> 00:59:22,060
I think I found her cute.

879
00:59:23,380 --> 00:59:25,440
She's not good at hiding.

880
00:59:25,440 --> 00:59:31,570
I noticed that she is inexperienced
in expressing emotions.

881
00:59:31,570 --> 00:59:34,800
That made her look cute at times.

882
00:59:35,790 --> 00:59:37,240
[The evening they moved in]

883
00:59:37,240 --> 00:59:38,820
I like it.

884
00:59:40,920 --> 00:59:45,620
She seems a little clumsy.

885
00:59:45,620 --> 00:59:48,600
Let's set aside a little...

886
00:59:49,490 --> 00:59:52,180
It's okay. It's okay.

887
00:59:56,410 --> 00:59:58,160
It's okay.

888
01:00:00,400 --> 01:00:02,300
Cheer up.

889
01:00:02,300 --> 01:00:03,900
Okay.

890
01:00:05,380 --> 01:00:07,660
And I thought that was cute.

891
01:00:07,660 --> 01:00:12,910
When I told her that, she froze instantly.

892
01:00:12,910 --> 01:00:16,220
She was like, "What was that?"

893
01:00:17,620 --> 01:00:22,020
She tried to change the subject clumsily.

894
01:00:22,990 --> 01:00:25,760
And I find that cute again.

895
01:00:25,760 --> 01:00:27,820
I can't read you.

896
01:00:27,820 --> 01:00:29,610
You can't?

897
01:00:30,560 --> 01:00:32,150
I can't.

898
01:00:33,350 --> 01:00:34,800
Really?

899
01:00:35,720 --> 01:00:37,530
I can't really tell.

900
01:00:39,830 --> 01:00:44,580
I first noticed that
on our first Sunday date.

901
01:00:46,610 --> 01:00:49,320
I got excited without realizing it.

902
01:00:54,140 --> 01:00:59,620
When I turned the corner and
checked who my date was,

903
01:01:03,140 --> 01:01:07,000
I couldn't help but laugh.

904
01:01:07,000 --> 01:01:09,800
I started laughing from a distance.

905
01:01:09,800 --> 01:01:13,630
I realized I was hoping for Yu Gyeong.

906
01:01:13,630 --> 01:01:15,850
- What's the deal?
- What?

907
01:01:15,850 --> 01:01:17,120
It's nothing.

908
01:01:17,120 --> 01:01:18,800
- Did you read it?
- Yes.

909
01:01:18,800 --> 01:01:21,120
- Shall we?
- Let's go.

910
01:01:22,540 --> 01:01:24,770
Do you know the expression,
"If you find someone cute, it's over"?

911
01:01:24,770 --> 01:01:26,620
I do.

912
01:01:32,160 --> 01:01:33,530
It's over.

913
01:01:34,560 --> 01:01:36,390
What?

914
01:01:36,390 --> 01:01:38,450
You're cute. I mean it.

915
01:01:39,730 --> 01:01:41,680
You're unstoppable.

916
01:01:46,280 --> 01:01:49,710
[On the way back from Gunsan]

917
01:01:54,650 --> 01:01:57,910
[Suppressing]

918
01:02:08,120 --> 01:02:12,050
["I like you"]

919
01:02:12,050 --> 01:02:14,150
["Me, too"]

920
01:02:21,400 --> 01:02:24,310
- I thought you were crying.
- No, no.

921
01:02:25,150 --> 01:02:30,220
[Did Wu Yeol's true feelings come through?]

922
01:02:32,490 --> 01:02:35,370
[Tearing up]

923
01:02:35,370 --> 01:02:37,960
[Tsuki, again?]

924
01:02:37,960 --> 01:02:40,900
She keeps... She keeps...

925
01:02:40,900 --> 01:02:43,800
- I was hearing noises.
- It's Tsuki time.

926
01:02:43,800 --> 01:02:46,790
It turns out she was crying.
Why are you crying?

927
01:02:46,790 --> 01:02:49,730
He wrote her a letter.

928
01:02:49,730 --> 01:02:52,720
It's so moving when someone changes.

929
01:02:52,720 --> 01:02:55,050
Tsuki is vicariously living through this.

930
01:02:55,050 --> 01:02:58,750
- I'm Yu Gyeong right now.
- You won't have to date for three years.

931
01:02:58,750 --> 01:03:01,790
- Team Seo Won with Seo Won.
- I love it.

932
01:03:01,790 --> 01:03:04,710
[The tenants are on their last outing]

933
01:03:04,710 --> 01:03:08,190
- Are they going out for dinner?
- Is it their last outing?

934
01:03:08,190 --> 01:03:09,180
Who is driving?

935
01:03:09,180 --> 01:03:11,980
- Seo Won, can I sit in the front?
- Go ahead, go ahead.

936
01:03:11,980 --> 01:03:14,930
[Seong Min and Seo Won
are driving separately]

937
01:03:15,490 --> 01:03:20,530
- This is my first time in this car.
- I've never been in the back seat.

938
01:03:20,530 --> 01:03:22,810
- Everyone's buckled up, right?
- Yes.

939
01:03:22,810 --> 01:03:24,690
Here we go.

940
01:03:25,690 --> 01:03:28,490
[Headed to their last dinner location]

941
01:03:28,490 --> 01:03:30,910
Everyone is sad.

942
01:03:33,050 --> 01:03:38,140
- My gosh.
- This must be so tough on everyone.

943
01:03:38,140 --> 01:03:40,630
I experienced all kinds of emotions here.

944
01:03:42,100 --> 01:03:44,890
- I think today was the hardest.
- Of course.

945
01:03:44,890 --> 01:03:48,490
Didn't we say and hear everything today?

946
01:03:48,490 --> 01:03:53,740
Yes, I finally learned my feelings today.

947
01:03:55,280 --> 01:03:58,440
I learned the other's feelings today, too.

948
01:03:58,440 --> 01:04:03,160
- I know.
- So Yun, listen.

949
01:04:12,730 --> 01:04:14,810
Is he waving at the other car?

950
01:04:14,810 --> 01:04:16,670
So cute.

951
01:04:17,670 --> 01:04:19,250
Is that the car behind us?

952
01:04:19,250 --> 01:04:21,390
[The two cars run into each other]

953
01:04:22,600 --> 01:04:25,850
They're there. Hello, handsome.

954
01:04:25,850 --> 01:04:28,020
Where are you going? Where are you going?

955
01:04:28,020 --> 01:04:29,790
- Where are you going?
- Where are you going?

956
01:04:29,790 --> 01:04:32,500
- Should we grab a bite?
- Sounds good.

957
01:04:32,500 --> 01:04:35,410
- Where?
- Sinjeon Tteokbokki?

958
01:04:35,410 --> 01:04:37,640
- Sin!
- I'm excited!

959
01:04:37,640 --> 01:04:40,060
- Jeon!
- I'm so excited!

960
01:04:40,060 --> 01:04:41,660
[Smiling]

961
01:04:44,300 --> 01:04:47,900
Yu Gyeong, they're taking a video.

962
01:04:49,050 --> 01:04:50,900
Who's taking it now?

963
01:04:51,810 --> 01:04:54,240
Gyu Ri must be taking it.

964
01:04:57,670 --> 01:04:59,370
So cute.

965
01:05:02,200 --> 01:05:04,490
So Yun is a bit...

966
01:05:04,490 --> 01:05:07,520
How do you do the Japanese dance?

967
01:05:07,520 --> 01:05:09,170
[Suddenly, dance time]

968
01:05:09,170 --> 01:05:10,320
[Smiling]

969
01:05:11,900 --> 01:05:14,320
Why do they look so sad in the end?

970
01:05:14,320 --> 01:05:18,320
I know. Maybe they think they
won't hang out like that again.

971
01:05:18,320 --> 01:05:19,750
Right.

972
01:05:21,850 --> 01:05:25,310
[The day is already ending]

973
01:05:27,970 --> 01:05:31,860
- This is a famous bridge.
- I want to go to Namsan.

974
01:05:31,860 --> 01:05:33,960
The sun is setting on the last day.

975
01:05:33,960 --> 01:05:36,070
We are seeing the sunset.

976
01:05:36,970 --> 01:05:39,990
I'll be a better person!

977
01:05:39,990 --> 01:05:42,240
I'll be a better person!

978
01:05:42,240 --> 01:05:44,820
Could we say it together just once?

979
01:05:44,820 --> 01:05:46,080
One, two, three!

980
01:05:46,080 --> 01:05:49,040
I'll be a better person!

981
01:05:49,040 --> 01:05:51,950
- I mean it!
- I don't think I can be better.

982
01:05:51,950 --> 01:05:56,490
- I think I'm fine.
- Let's keep it moderate.

983
01:05:56,490 --> 01:05:58,740
Which place is it?

984
01:05:58,740 --> 01:06:00,340
This place is pretty.

985
01:06:00,340 --> 01:06:03,560
[An Italian restaurant in Yongsan-gu]

986
01:06:04,980 --> 01:06:07,680
So pretty.

987
01:06:07,680 --> 01:06:10,420
What? Hold on.

988
01:06:10,420 --> 01:06:11,900
[Stylish Italian dishes]

989
01:06:11,900 --> 01:06:13,770
Is this the Last Supper?

990
01:06:13,770 --> 01:06:15,790
The steak looks so tasty.

991
01:06:15,790 --> 01:06:17,150
What a great spread.

992
01:06:17,150 --> 01:06:21,180
- The last banquet.
- I hope they enjoy it.

993
01:06:25,210 --> 01:06:26,830
The view is amazing.

994
01:06:26,830 --> 01:06:29,870
- The view is crazy here.
- The view from that window is the best.

995
01:06:29,870 --> 01:06:32,020
Daebak.

996
01:06:32,020 --> 01:06:35,920
- Can we eat now?
- Thank you for the meal.

997
01:06:36,770 --> 01:06:37,760
[Mm]

998
01:06:39,720 --> 01:06:42,090
It's our last meal together.

999
01:06:42,090 --> 01:06:44,440
It's okay to gain weight. Eat a lot.

1000
01:06:46,080 --> 01:06:46,870
[Clearing throat]

1001
01:06:47,900 --> 01:06:50,400
You want to raise glasses together.

1002
01:06:51,300 --> 01:06:55,650
- You all did so well.
- We really did.

1003
01:06:55,650 --> 01:06:57,310
What was the most memorable moment?

1004
01:06:57,310 --> 01:06:58,620
I like that.

1005
01:06:58,620 --> 01:07:00,490
To me, it was Yunnori.

1006
01:07:00,490 --> 01:07:02,290
Right, that was so fun.

1007
01:07:02,290 --> 01:07:05,620
Jun Hyeon wouldn't let me have the yut.

1008
01:07:05,620 --> 01:07:07,020
Did I?

1009
01:07:07,020 --> 01:07:08,340
"No, no!"

1010
01:07:08,340 --> 01:07:11,670
- We got so emotional.
- Right.

1011
01:07:11,670 --> 01:07:13,160
[The controversial Yunnori moment]

1012
01:07:14,310 --> 01:07:15,530
[The yut is on the edge of the blanket]

1013
01:07:15,530 --> 01:07:18,490
- It's out.
- It's out. It's out. It's halfway over.

1014
01:07:18,490 --> 01:07:20,800
How is that out?

1015
01:07:20,800 --> 01:07:22,900
It's game over.

1016
01:07:22,900 --> 01:07:24,370
Time out.

1017
01:07:25,250 --> 01:07:26,920
Move your hands.

1018
01:07:26,920 --> 01:07:29,620
National Forensic Service? They say it's out.

1019
01:07:29,620 --> 01:07:31,620
How could that be out?

1020
01:07:31,620 --> 01:07:33,670
[The criminal attorney won't stop arguing]

1021
01:07:33,670 --> 01:07:35,430
How is this in?

1022
01:07:35,430 --> 01:07:38,180
Let's be honest, it's out. Look.

1023
01:07:38,180 --> 01:07:42,830
[A ruthless game of Yunnori]

1024
01:07:42,830 --> 01:07:46,490
- What a mess.
- It wasn't there. It was here.

1025
01:07:47,490 --> 01:07:49,570
[Embarrassed]

1026
01:07:49,570 --> 01:07:51,380
It felt amazing receiving the bow.

1027
01:07:51,380 --> 01:07:54,110
- Oh, the bow.
- Sorry.

1028
01:07:54,110 --> 01:07:57,040
[A little late, but a heartwarming ending]

1029
01:07:58,550 --> 01:08:00,970
[The women gathered in the
living room the other day]

1030
01:08:00,970 --> 01:08:02,620
[Scratching]

1031
01:08:02,620 --> 01:08:04,190
Come on.

1032
01:08:04,190 --> 01:08:07,010
I feel like she's my daughter. Come here.

1033
01:08:07,010 --> 01:08:10,000
My baby.

1034
01:08:10,000 --> 01:08:12,470
Unni.

1035
01:08:13,400 --> 01:08:16,040
I hear a cow.

1036
01:08:16,040 --> 01:08:18,910
[Tea time in the living room]

1037
01:08:22,460 --> 01:08:24,100
Come here.

1038
01:08:26,650 --> 01:08:29,310
- Come here.
- I need to be scratched.

1039
01:08:29,310 --> 01:08:31,480
[Scratching]

1040
01:08:31,480 --> 01:08:34,070
My Yu Gyeong. Scratch, scratch.

1041
01:08:35,000 --> 01:08:38,130
- I must smell.
- You don't.

1042
01:08:38,130 --> 01:08:41,560
- Unni!
- Yes, Yu Gyeong.

1043
01:08:44,930 --> 01:08:47,060
[Crying after being home alone]

1044
01:08:47,060 --> 01:08:49,350
Come here, my puppy.

1045
01:08:54,150 --> 01:08:56,380
I'm home now.

1046
01:08:56,380 --> 01:08:58,560
You're going out again.

1047
01:09:00,830 --> 01:09:03,020
- Someone's here.
- What?

1048
01:09:04,820 --> 01:09:08,230
- Unni. Unni.
- Who is it?

1049
01:09:08,230 --> 01:09:09,400
It's Min Ju.

1050
01:09:09,400 --> 01:09:12,670
- Gosh, why are you back so soon?
- I think I'm going to cry.

1051
01:09:12,670 --> 01:09:13,880
Hi!

1052
01:09:13,880 --> 01:09:16,740
Good work today. You look so cute today.

1053
01:09:16,740 --> 01:09:19,200
No, I don't. It's my work outfit.

1054
01:09:19,200 --> 01:09:22,190
- You look pretty.
- Do I? What were you guys up to?

1055
01:09:22,190 --> 01:09:24,230
What's with your OOTD?

1056
01:09:24,230 --> 01:09:27,670
Chic? Is it an interview look?

1057
01:09:28,780 --> 01:09:32,680
- It's because he always wears a suit.
- You're right.

1058
01:09:32,680 --> 01:09:36,530
I have a question. Why don't you
change when you're home?

1059
01:09:36,530 --> 01:09:38,590
You didn't get to see my outfit.

1060
01:09:40,650 --> 01:09:43,420
Gosh, what's wrong with him?

1061
01:09:43,420 --> 01:09:44,900
You didn't get to see my outfit.

1062
01:09:44,900 --> 01:09:47,570
He keeps me on my toes.

1063
01:09:47,570 --> 01:09:49,700
She says he keeps her on her toes.

1064
01:09:49,700 --> 01:09:52,610
There is an amazing barbecue spot.

1065
01:09:52,610 --> 01:09:54,690
We'll totally dress down.

1066
01:09:54,690 --> 01:09:57,840
- But I'll be there after work.
- You're right.

1067
01:09:57,840 --> 01:10:02,630
Will you be dressed like this?
Gosh, it's suffocating.

1068
01:10:02,630 --> 01:10:05,060
You look cute. Are you matching with him?

1069
01:10:05,060 --> 01:10:06,790
You're a suit couple.

1070
01:10:06,790 --> 01:10:10,410
Come here. Let me roll you.

1071
01:10:10,410 --> 01:10:14,180
[Powerful lint rolling]

1072
01:10:14,180 --> 01:10:17,590
- All done.
- Thank you.

1073
01:10:17,590 --> 01:10:21,690
- You're ready for a date.
- Have a good date.

1074
01:10:21,690 --> 01:10:23,440
Have a good date.

1075
01:10:23,440 --> 01:10:27,320
[The women's room
is always filled with laughter]

1076
01:10:27,320 --> 01:10:30,300
It was fun when Queen Jun Hyeon joined us.

1077
01:10:30,300 --> 01:10:34,010
- We talked under the same blanket.
- Really?

1078
01:10:34,010 --> 01:10:36,800
I'm wondering if I was mistaken.

1079
01:10:36,800 --> 01:10:39,660
- He probably meant it in that moment.
- Right, right.

1080
01:10:39,660 --> 01:10:41,650
You don't know that.

1081
01:10:41,650 --> 01:10:43,020
He's so dependable.

1082
01:10:43,020 --> 01:10:46,880
You never know what would happen
with a disarming man like that.

1083
01:10:46,880 --> 01:10:48,890
Queen Jun Hyeon.

1084
01:10:48,890 --> 01:10:51,390
Queen? I like it.

1085
01:10:51,390 --> 01:10:53,640
- Jun Hyeon is popular.
- He's sensible.

1086
01:10:53,640 --> 01:10:56,090
What's wrong with him?

1087
01:10:56,090 --> 01:10:57,990
Don't get too comfortable yet, Oppa.

1088
01:10:57,990 --> 01:11:00,990
- We are not at that stage yet.
- Close.

1089
01:11:00,990 --> 01:11:04,360
I always join you for the girls' talk.

1090
01:11:04,360 --> 01:11:06,950
Do you have spare pajamas?

1091
01:11:08,810 --> 01:11:11,570
I'm so curious. We didn't know.

1092
01:11:11,570 --> 01:11:13,640
We know nothing about it.

1093
01:11:13,640 --> 01:11:18,170
[Their private happy memories]

1094
01:11:18,170 --> 01:11:20,690
This is why everyone likes Jun Hyeon.

1095
01:11:20,690 --> 01:11:24,490
He's not easy, but he puts you at ease.

1096
01:11:26,670 --> 01:11:28,480
What is it...

1097
01:11:31,210 --> 01:11:33,780
So pretty.

1098
01:11:33,780 --> 01:11:37,190
[The tenants are on the rooftop]

1099
01:11:38,010 --> 01:11:40,340
Should we sit?

1100
01:11:40,340 --> 01:11:43,050
- The view is amazing.
- I'm wide awake now.

1101
01:11:43,050 --> 01:11:45,490
What nice weather.

1102
01:11:49,320 --> 01:11:50,910
I feel sad.

1103
01:11:52,400 --> 01:11:55,560
[The fact that it's over is hitting them]

1104
01:11:55,560 --> 01:11:58,810
Although it's over...
It's sad that it's over, but...

1105
01:11:58,810 --> 01:12:00,560
[Smiling]

1106
01:12:08,150 --> 01:12:11,200
I just feel grateful.

1107
01:12:13,260 --> 01:12:15,470
This is fate.

1108
01:12:15,470 --> 01:12:17,740
It was harder than I expected,

1109
01:12:17,740 --> 01:12:22,230
but I was also happier than I expected.

1110
01:12:22,230 --> 01:12:24,750
Don't you crave Muktaekkang*?
(Korean chips)

1111
01:12:24,750 --> 01:12:28,670
That and Choco Songi and Kancho.

1112
01:12:30,590 --> 01:12:36,080
[He leaves as soon as he hears Min Ju]

1113
01:12:44,150 --> 01:12:46,160
[He always kept stock
of Min Ju's favorite snacks]

1114
01:12:46,160 --> 01:12:47,880
He went and bought the snacks.

1115
01:12:47,880 --> 01:12:51,760
I'd go weak in the knees
if someone bought me snacks.

1116
01:12:51,760 --> 01:12:53,190
You want to go out?

1117
01:12:53,190 --> 01:12:54,660
- Where?
- For a drive.

1118
01:12:54,660 --> 01:12:55,990
I'd love to.

1119
01:12:55,990 --> 01:12:58,060
I was wondering if you were home alone.

1120
01:12:58,060 --> 01:12:59,350
I wondered on my way home.

1121
01:12:59,350 --> 01:13:01,540
Good thing I didn't go out.

1122
01:13:01,540 --> 01:13:05,420
[Seong Min swiftly returned home]

1123
01:13:05,990 --> 01:13:11,040
I think we unintentionally hurt
one another without even knowing it.

1124
01:13:11,040 --> 01:13:13,210
Sort my feelings?

1125
01:13:13,210 --> 01:13:15,950
Honestly, there's nothing to sort.

1126
01:13:15,950 --> 01:13:18,630
I continue to like Seong Min.

1127
01:13:18,630 --> 01:13:22,440
But let's forget about all that

1128
01:13:22,440 --> 01:13:25,770
and meet up and have fun.

1129
01:13:27,310 --> 01:13:29,490
This is just the start.

1130
01:13:29,490 --> 01:13:32,780
- For real.
- This is just the start.

1131
01:13:32,780 --> 01:13:34,600
Exactly.

1132
01:13:41,150 --> 01:13:43,320
Gosh, he's handsome.

1133
01:13:46,190 --> 01:13:48,450
Actually...

1134
01:13:49,530 --> 01:13:53,260
So Yun can't take her eyes off him.

1135
01:13:53,260 --> 01:13:57,530
I put on a brave face and cracked
jokes to mask how I really felt, but...

1136
01:13:58,820 --> 01:14:01,650
Do you enjoy cleaning?
This is very important.

1137
01:14:01,650 --> 01:14:03,020
- I don't.
- You like to?

1138
01:14:03,020 --> 01:14:04,130
- I don't like to.
- You don't?

1139
01:14:04,130 --> 01:14:06,820
- Do you?
- I really don't like to.

1140
01:14:06,820 --> 01:14:09,960
- I was really worried about that.
- Really?

1141
01:14:11,120 --> 01:14:15,950
[When Seo Won had zero votes]

1142
01:14:15,950 --> 01:14:20,410
We found out later that we both
pretended to have received texts.

1143
01:14:21,730 --> 01:14:24,350
[Stares]

1144
01:14:25,380 --> 01:14:28,070
What are you staring at so happily?

1145
01:14:30,200 --> 01:14:31,920
[Evades answer]

1146
01:14:32,570 --> 01:14:34,790
We end up controlling our expressions.

1147
01:14:34,790 --> 01:14:38,560
We tried to hide the fact
that no one texted us.

1148
01:14:38,560 --> 01:14:41,480
That was pretty funny.

1149
01:14:42,320 --> 01:14:45,770
[Turmoil 1]

1150
01:14:45,770 --> 01:14:48,770
[Turmoil 2]

1151
01:14:49,540 --> 01:14:52,240
We came looking for love.

1152
01:14:52,240 --> 01:14:54,920
I can do it. Fighting!

1153
01:14:55,920 --> 01:14:57,600
Fighting, Seo Won!

1154
01:14:57,600 --> 01:15:00,150
[With positive energy]

1155
01:15:00,150 --> 01:15:01,830
You can do it, Seo Won.

1156
01:15:01,830 --> 01:15:03,710
You can do it!

1157
01:15:03,710 --> 01:15:06,560
But I'm so upset...

1158
01:15:06,560 --> 01:15:08,670
Let's do this.

1159
01:15:08,670 --> 01:15:10,160
Fighting!

1160
01:15:12,730 --> 01:15:16,100
- I really had a hard time.
- That's right. We saw it all.

1161
01:15:16,100 --> 01:15:23,100
[Two women resided in Seo Won's heart]

1162
01:15:29,170 --> 01:15:33,020
[Seo Won wrote down his
chaotic feelings in his journal]

1163
01:15:33,020 --> 01:15:35,490
[I wasn't always just happy.
I was sad, lonely, tired...]

1164
01:15:35,490 --> 01:15:38,980
I can't imagine
how hard it must've been for him.

1165
01:15:38,980 --> 01:15:42,090
[I knew it'd be an emotional roller coaster,
but it's a bit harder than I thought]

1166
01:15:42,090 --> 01:15:44,670
I bet it's more than just a bit.

1167
01:15:45,920 --> 01:15:50,600
After our last one-on-one conversations,

1168
01:15:50,600 --> 01:15:54,790
I was waiting in my room and saw the
bed that I'll no longer sleep on.

1169
01:15:54,790 --> 01:15:57,410
He's crying about his bed?

1170
01:15:58,380 --> 01:16:03,010
- I've become attached to everyone.
- He cries so naturally.

1171
01:16:03,010 --> 01:16:04,800
He's so pure.

1172
01:16:04,800 --> 01:16:07,730
Thank you for treating me so nicely.

1173
01:16:09,950 --> 01:16:11,420
[Cries]

1174
01:16:13,610 --> 01:16:16,230
He's so sincere.

1175
01:16:16,230 --> 01:16:18,490
Thank you.

1176
01:16:18,490 --> 01:16:21,280
Sorry. Sorry...

1177
01:16:22,130 --> 01:16:23,490
Hush.

1178
01:16:24,490 --> 01:16:26,620
You cried a lot, too.

1179
01:16:27,720 --> 01:16:30,620
The two of them were sobbing.

1180
01:16:31,870 --> 01:16:33,690
Thank you so much.

1181
01:16:34,660 --> 01:16:36,230
[Tearing]

1182
01:16:36,230 --> 01:16:38,990
- So Yun is crying, too.
- Oh, no.

1183
01:16:38,990 --> 01:16:40,540
I wish they end up together.

1184
01:16:40,540 --> 01:16:42,050
[Stares]

1185
01:16:42,050 --> 01:16:43,640
I know.

1186
01:16:45,870 --> 01:16:48,310
Why are you looking at me?

1187
01:16:49,350 --> 01:16:53,120
- Let's have a glass.
- You're so cute.

1188
01:16:53,120 --> 01:16:59,340
[The final toast, full of tears]

1189
01:17:00,040 --> 01:17:03,020
- It got warm all of a sudden.
- I know.

1190
01:17:03,020 --> 01:17:05,860
The ending should be heartwarming.

1191
01:17:07,920 --> 01:17:09,120
What is it?

1192
01:17:09,120 --> 01:17:13,370
[Call your final choice to your own special
spot and express your feelings]

1193
01:17:15,190 --> 01:17:16,850
Your own special spot?

1194
01:17:16,850 --> 01:17:20,140
- The time has come.
- Finally.

1195
01:17:22,060 --> 01:17:24,900
[In the cold city winter]

1196
01:17:24,900 --> 01:17:32,700
[we loved fiercely and ached deeply]

1197
01:17:35,010 --> 01:17:40,340
[Laughing like a child at times]

1198
01:17:40,340 --> 01:17:45,330
[Facing feelings that grew deeper by the day]

1199
01:17:45,330 --> 01:17:50,670
My eyes were drawn to you the most.

1200
01:17:50,670 --> 01:17:53,730
[The moments I dove into the unknown,
relying solely on myself]

1201
01:17:56,700 --> 01:18:02,790
[Finding the most authentic version
of myself]

1202
01:18:04,630 --> 01:18:08,260
[And enduring the pain and confusion within]

1203
01:18:10,640 --> 01:18:13,940
[In between the passing days]

1204
01:18:13,940 --> 01:18:17,830
[Who was the one who helped me to breathe?]

1205
01:18:19,610 --> 01:18:26,300
[Amidst a sea of emotions,
a single truth blossoms]

1206
01:18:26,300 --> 01:18:29,460
[The final choice is revealed now]

1207
01:18:29,460 --> 01:18:34,340
[Did you detect their heart signals?]

1208
01:18:34,340 --> 01:18:40,050
[Predict the eight people's
final choices based on clues!]

1209
01:18:40,050 --> 01:18:42,140
I don't want it to end.

1210
01:18:42,140 --> 01:18:43,700
It's time for their final choices.

1211
01:18:43,700 --> 01:18:48,230
Reviewing their emotions, we'll predict
their choices, one by one.

1212
01:18:48,230 --> 01:18:51,110
How can it be the end already? I'm so sad.

1213
01:18:51,110 --> 01:18:52,910
Let's get the final predictions right.

1214
01:18:52,910 --> 01:18:54,650
I'm confident we can.

1215
01:18:54,650 --> 01:18:56,160
It's the end already?

1216
01:18:56,160 --> 01:18:59,510
- Let's start with the easiest.
- The easiest.

1217
01:18:59,510 --> 01:19:01,740
That would be Park Wu Yeol and Yu Gyeong.

1218
01:19:01,740 --> 01:19:03,590
They were really special.

1219
01:19:03,590 --> 01:19:07,350
My heart ached every time I watched them.

1220
01:19:07,350 --> 01:19:10,750
The person who changed me the most.

1221
01:19:10,750 --> 01:19:13,060
- It's 100%.
- Easy, easy.

1222
01:19:13,060 --> 01:19:14,410
Yu Gyeong is easy, too.

1223
01:19:14,410 --> 01:19:16,190
Kang Yu Gyeong, cross!

1224
01:19:16,190 --> 01:19:20,080
I have the most fun when I'm with you.

1225
01:19:20,080 --> 01:19:22,380
There's also Jun Hyeon
who opens the door for her.

1226
01:19:22,380 --> 01:19:23,750
That's right.

1227
01:19:23,750 --> 01:19:26,330
[Could it be Jun Hyeon
who was always by her side?]

1228
01:19:26,330 --> 01:19:28,450
A man who's gentle and sweet.

1229
01:19:28,450 --> 01:19:31,960
- Are we wrong? Think about it.
- Give me five seconds.

1230
01:19:31,960 --> 01:19:33,340
But do you remember?

1231
01:19:33,340 --> 01:19:38,340
"He shouldn't be so pale,
or his lips shouldn't be so red."

1232
01:19:38,340 --> 01:19:39,480
But Yu Gyeong...

1233
01:19:39,480 --> 01:19:42,460
- Until the end!
- Wu Yeol?

1234
01:19:42,460 --> 01:19:44,810
Today is the last day for our arrows.

1235
01:19:44,810 --> 01:19:47,060
Kang Yu Gyeong and Park Wu Yeol.

1236
01:19:47,060 --> 01:19:49,490
- Now...
- Jeong Jun Hyeon is easy.

1237
01:19:49,490 --> 01:19:53,230
There was only one person the
whole time. It was Yu Gyeong.

1238
01:19:53,230 --> 01:19:54,910
Jeong Jun Hyeon and Kang Yu Gyeong.

1239
01:19:54,910 --> 01:19:58,470
Jeong Jun Hyeon and Kang Yu Gyeong. I agree.

1240
01:19:58,470 --> 01:20:00,340
- So Yun and Seo Won?
- Seo Won.

1241
01:20:00,340 --> 01:20:01,990
- So Yun and Seo Won.
- They're so good together.

1242
01:20:01,990 --> 01:20:05,690
I'm so regretful.
I should've been more selfish.

1243
01:20:05,690 --> 01:20:09,040
- So Yun and Seo Won.
- Totally.

1244
01:20:09,040 --> 01:20:12,920
- And Min Ju?
- It's Seong Min.

1245
01:20:12,920 --> 01:20:16,130
[Min Ju was always honest about her feelings]

1246
01:20:16,130 --> 01:20:18,850
- Right?
- Min Ju and Seong Min.

1247
01:20:20,840 --> 01:20:23,500
- And Seong Min...
- Seong Min is hard.

1248
01:20:23,500 --> 01:20:25,110
Seong Min is hard.

1249
01:20:25,110 --> 01:20:27,570
- I think it's Yu Gyeong, but...
- Me, too.

1250
01:20:27,570 --> 01:20:30,580
Seong Min knows it won't work out,
but I think he'll still choose her.

1251
01:20:30,580 --> 01:20:35,900
I guess you can say being devoted
from beginning to end was his crime.

1252
01:20:35,900 --> 01:20:37,800
Let's choose Yu Gyeong.

1253
01:20:37,800 --> 01:20:41,630
But when they had their final
one-on-one conversation...

1254
01:20:41,630 --> 01:20:45,160
When Min Ju and Seong Min
had their one-on-one,

1255
01:20:45,160 --> 01:20:48,290
I felt subtle lingering feelings.

1256
01:20:48,290 --> 01:20:51,290
It was more apologetic
than lingering feelings.

1257
01:20:51,290 --> 01:20:53,910
When Seong Min spoke his last words,

1258
01:20:53,910 --> 01:20:56,010
what he expressed was gratitude.

1259
01:20:56,010 --> 01:20:57,840
Gratitude equals goodbye.

1260
01:20:57,840 --> 01:21:00,320
He couldn't bring himself to choose Min Ju.

1261
01:21:00,320 --> 01:21:01,680
Okay! Yu Gyeong!

1262
01:21:01,680 --> 01:21:05,390
- Yu Gyeong.
- This is right.

1263
01:21:05,390 --> 01:21:09,250
Yu Gyeong got all the votes until the end.

1264
01:21:09,250 --> 01:21:10,400
Let's do Gyu Ri next.

1265
01:21:10,400 --> 01:21:12,580
Gyu Ri will choose Seo Won.

1266
01:21:12,580 --> 01:21:15,140
- Gyu Ri and Seo Won.
- I think Gyu Ri will choose Seo Won.

1267
01:21:15,140 --> 01:21:17,590
Now it's Seo Won's turn. The last one.

1268
01:21:17,590 --> 01:21:19,300
I have to think about this one.

1269
01:21:19,300 --> 01:21:20,620
- Really?
- I know.

1270
01:21:20,620 --> 01:21:22,130
I really have to think about this.

1271
01:21:22,130 --> 01:21:26,850
Seo Won cried his heart out
while talking with So Yun.

1272
01:21:26,850 --> 01:21:28,663
- But I think it's Gyu Ri.
- It's Gyu Ri.

1273
01:21:28,663 --> 01:21:29,980
Seo Won can't help it.

1274
01:21:29,980 --> 01:21:31,405
- It's not So Yun?
- Really?

1275
01:21:31,405 --> 01:21:34,495
Why do you think he cried so hard?

1276
01:21:35,390 --> 01:21:37,930
- He feels bad for So Yun.
- You're right.

1277
01:21:37,930 --> 01:21:40,330
Oh, no.

1278
01:21:40,330 --> 01:21:41,920
That's so sad.

1279
01:21:41,920 --> 01:21:44,950
- It's a shame.
- It really is.

1280
01:21:44,950 --> 01:21:47,900
I'm weak toward a man who cries like a child.

1281
01:21:47,900 --> 01:21:50,560
That's a wrap! We'll check the
results one by one.

1282
01:21:50,560 --> 01:21:51,990
Is this really the end?

1283
01:21:51,990 --> 01:21:54,600
The final results remain.

1284
01:21:54,600 --> 01:21:59,290
They call their final choice person.

1285
01:21:59,290 --> 01:22:04,280
If that person also chose them,
they will head over to meet that person.

1286
01:22:04,280 --> 01:22:06,270
Their choices will connect them
to each other.

1287
01:22:06,270 --> 01:22:08,700
I got butterflies.

1288
01:22:08,700 --> 01:22:12,870
- Min Ju's final choice!
- Oh, my gosh!

1289
01:22:14,900 --> 01:22:19,800
[One month passed by like a dream]

1290
01:22:19,800 --> 01:22:22,150
We all adore Min Ju so much.

1291
01:22:22,150 --> 01:22:23,870
Finally.

1292
01:22:25,470 --> 01:22:27,170
Oh, my gosh.

1293
01:22:27,170 --> 01:22:31,650
[My heart is racing]

1294
01:22:38,600 --> 01:22:40,190
Hello?

1295
01:22:41,110 --> 01:22:42,330
Oppa.

1296
01:22:42,330 --> 01:22:44,340
Oh, my gosh!

1297
01:22:44,340 --> 01:22:46,470
[We believe in you, Min Ju]

1298
01:22:47,800 --> 01:22:50,580
It's me. It's Min Ju.

1299
01:22:51,540 --> 01:22:52,940
It's Min Ju.

1300
01:22:52,940 --> 01:22:55,270
[Min Ju's final choice is Kim Seong Min]

1301
01:22:55,270 --> 01:22:58,250
Min Ju's final choice is Seong Min.

1302
01:22:58,250 --> 01:23:01,320
- Min Ju, until the end...
- That's impressive.

1303
01:23:01,320 --> 01:23:03,410
You can tell by my voice, right?

1304
01:23:03,410 --> 01:23:05,710
Right away.

1305
01:23:09,350 --> 01:23:12,740
We've made a lot of memories

1306
01:23:12,740 --> 01:23:17,490
and I'm feeling a mix of emotions right now.

1307
01:23:19,430 --> 01:23:21,510
This past month,

1308
01:23:23,790 --> 01:23:27,330
I think you were my everything.

1309
01:23:34,460 --> 01:23:39,260
- How is she like literal sunshine?
- Gosh, how could she...

1310
01:23:39,260 --> 01:23:42,220
[I'm going to cry again]

1311
01:23:43,910 --> 01:23:48,110
There were so many times when
all our overlapping coincidences

1312
01:23:48,110 --> 01:23:52,690
felt like we were truly destined.

1313
01:23:53,890 --> 01:24:00,580
Thank you for making my heart sing and race.

1314
01:24:04,700 --> 01:24:08,820
For this whole month...

1315
01:24:10,110 --> 01:24:12,300
from 1 to 10,

1316
01:24:12,300 --> 01:24:15,040
I'm endlessly thankful.

1317
01:24:18,100 --> 01:24:20,620
Thank you so much.

1318
01:24:21,630 --> 01:24:23,680
Let's see each other often in the real world.

1319
01:24:23,680 --> 01:24:24,950
Yeah.

1320
01:24:24,950 --> 01:24:26,700
Let's do that.

1321
01:24:28,710 --> 01:24:31,880
- She gave it her all.
- She's a romantic.

1322
01:24:33,540 --> 01:24:36,360
[Min Ju never wavered in her choice]

1323
01:24:36,360 --> 01:24:38,150
She was so great.

1324
01:24:39,030 --> 01:24:40,530
Tsuki is crying.

1325
01:24:40,530 --> 01:24:43,030
She said, "You were my everything."

1326
01:24:43,030 --> 01:24:46,130
We can see it, too.

1327
01:24:46,130 --> 01:24:48,640
Seong Min was crying a little bit, too.

1328
01:24:48,640 --> 01:24:51,640
Min Ju was so impactful on the phone call.

1329
01:24:51,640 --> 01:24:55,430
- "For a month, you were my everything."
- It's true.

1330
01:24:55,430 --> 01:24:57,990
She put down her pride
and told him her truth.

1331
01:24:57,990 --> 01:24:59,990
She has so much self-respect.

1332
01:25:00,630 --> 01:25:02,630
Who is Seong Min's final choice?

1333
01:25:02,630 --> 01:25:04,980
I hope it works out for those two.

1334
01:25:08,300 --> 01:25:12,670
[A month where they raced to find love]

1335
01:25:13,430 --> 01:25:16,560
[Min Ju stayed by his side at every moment]

1336
01:25:16,560 --> 01:25:19,960
- They look so good together!
- Gosh, they do.

1337
01:25:22,760 --> 01:25:24,030
[From the first meeting]

1338
01:25:24,900 --> 01:25:27,080
[He felt strong attraction toward Yu Gyeong]

1339
01:25:27,080 --> 01:25:29,630
I feel better about this.

1340
01:25:32,890 --> 01:25:35,100
Is it Min Ju or Yu Gyeong?

1341
01:25:35,100 --> 01:25:39,600
[What is his final destination
after a long journey?]

1342
01:25:52,330 --> 01:25:54,140
Hello?

1343
01:25:54,140 --> 01:25:55,420
Hello?

1344
01:25:56,110 --> 01:25:57,580
[Min Ju? Yu Gyeong?]

1345
01:25:58,450 --> 01:26:00,250
Hello?

1346
01:26:00,250 --> 01:26:01,740
Hello?

1347
01:26:01,740 --> 01:26:08,010
[Kim Seong Min's final choice
is Kang Yu Gyeong]

1348
01:26:08,010 --> 01:26:09,590
It's me.

1349
01:26:09,590 --> 01:26:12,330
Seong Min's final choice is Yu Gyeong.

1350
01:26:12,330 --> 01:26:14,710
I like this for Seong Min.

1351
01:26:14,710 --> 01:26:17,390
- It's honest.
- Thank goodness.

1352
01:26:20,460 --> 01:26:23,960
Looking back, thanks to you,

1353
01:26:23,960 --> 01:26:27,220
I laughed a lot. Really.

1354
01:26:29,890 --> 01:26:31,990
That's why I called you.

1355
01:26:35,810 --> 01:26:37,790
I'm laughing now, too.

1356
01:26:41,760 --> 01:26:45,630
Thank you so, so much.

1357
01:26:47,730 --> 01:26:49,980
Thank you, too.

1358
01:26:51,300 --> 01:26:54,830
That's how Seong Min gets closure.

1359
01:26:55,530 --> 01:26:58,170
You have to go with who you like.

1360
01:26:58,170 --> 01:27:00,360
He feels the way Min Ju does.

1361
01:27:00,360 --> 01:27:02,040
- It's the same thing.
- Right.

1362
01:27:02,040 --> 01:27:06,020
He wasn't the smoothest,
but he only had her in mind.

1363
01:27:06,020 --> 01:27:07,630
He meant it.

1364
01:27:07,630 --> 01:27:09,320
He went through a lot.

1365
01:27:09,320 --> 01:27:10,890
Good job.

1366
01:27:10,890 --> 01:27:12,230
[Choi So Yun's final choice]

1367
01:27:12,230 --> 01:27:14,910
Who is So Yun's final choice?

1368
01:27:21,400 --> 01:27:28,270
[So Yun was honest about her
feelings at every moment]

1369
01:27:29,260 --> 01:27:32,370
[Who is that one person
who warms your heart...]

1370
01:27:33,290 --> 01:27:36,310
[just at the thought of him?]

1371
01:27:36,960 --> 01:27:39,070
My goodness...

1372
01:27:46,570 --> 01:27:48,680
[Heart racing]

1373
01:27:48,680 --> 01:27:50,700
[Seo Won, right?]

1374
01:28:00,010 --> 01:28:02,010
Hello?

1375
01:28:03,250 --> 01:28:05,250
What?

1376
01:28:05,250 --> 01:28:07,620
Is it Jun Hyeon? His voice...

1377
01:28:07,620 --> 01:28:09,330
Hello?

1378
01:28:11,700 --> 01:28:18,530
[Choi So Yun's final choice is Kim Seo Won]

1379
01:28:18,530 --> 01:28:20,220
- It's not.
- No way.

1380
01:28:20,220 --> 01:28:23,070
We saw it in her eyes.

1381
01:28:23,070 --> 01:28:26,310
So Yun's final choice is Seo Won.

1382
01:28:28,320 --> 01:28:31,220
During this short time,

1383
01:28:31,220 --> 01:28:34,170
I'm thankful to you for so much.

1384
01:28:37,070 --> 01:28:38,990
In my eyes,

1385
01:28:42,300 --> 01:28:48,760
you were the coolest for expressing
everything so honestly.

1386
01:28:48,760 --> 01:28:50,430
My goodness.

1387
01:28:52,170 --> 01:28:57,340
So, just like how you gave me courage,

1388
01:28:59,060 --> 01:29:04,110
I hope my feelings
can be courage for you, too.

1389
01:29:05,670 --> 01:29:08,550
She's so great with words.

1390
01:29:10,030 --> 01:29:13,640
I will root for all the choices you make.

1391
01:29:15,180 --> 01:29:18,220
- She's so good with words.
- It's crazy.

1392
01:29:19,340 --> 01:29:21,510
Stay strong, Kim Seo Won!

1393
01:29:22,920 --> 01:29:24,460
Noona...

1394
01:29:24,460 --> 01:29:27,440
[Choking up]

1395
01:29:31,990 --> 01:29:37,350
[Seo Won was one and only for So Yun]

1396
01:29:39,510 --> 01:29:41,390
[Teary]

1397
01:29:41,390 --> 01:29:44,040
So Yun's final choice is Seo Won.

1398
01:29:44,040 --> 01:29:46,210
We predicted that, too.

1399
01:29:46,210 --> 01:29:48,760
"I will root for all the choices you make."

1400
01:29:48,760 --> 01:29:51,050
Seo Won and So Yun look so good together.

1401
01:29:51,050 --> 01:29:53,330
Two interesting characters.

1402
01:29:53,330 --> 01:29:56,710
Let's find out right away.

1403
01:29:56,710 --> 01:29:58,780
Who is Seo Won's final choice?

1404
01:29:58,780 --> 01:30:02,100
- I can't watch this.
- Seo Won...

1405
01:30:02,100 --> 01:30:05,640
[Kim Seo Won's final choice]

1406
01:30:05,640 --> 01:30:09,650
I don't care if we're wrong.
I want him to show up like a movie.

1407
01:30:09,650 --> 01:30:16,250
[Love was everything this month,
every nervous moment precious]

1408
01:30:17,440 --> 01:30:25,430
[When you follow your heart,
who is there at the end?]

1409
01:30:25,430 --> 01:30:28,900
- Seo Won is debating, too.
- Yes, he is.

1410
01:30:39,130 --> 01:30:41,230
- Hello?
- Hello?

1411
01:30:41,230 --> 01:30:44,850
- No way.
- Is it Gyu Ri or So Yun?

1412
01:30:46,570 --> 01:30:48,820
Noona, it's me.

1413
01:30:48,820 --> 01:30:50,610
[Which noona?]

1414
01:30:50,610 --> 01:30:53,020
[Will Seo So Yun happen?]

1415
01:30:53,020 --> 01:30:54,820
Noona, it's me.

1416
01:30:55,600 --> 01:31:00,300
[Kim Seo Won's final choice is Jeong Gyu Ri]

1417
01:31:00,300 --> 01:31:03,640
Seo Won's final choice is Gyu Ri.

1418
01:31:03,640 --> 01:31:06,260
Seo Won followed his own path, too.

1419
01:31:06,260 --> 01:31:08,620
- He did.
- Right.

1420
01:31:13,680 --> 01:31:15,950
I'm so nervous.

1421
01:31:20,280 --> 01:31:23,470
I thought I would always give it my all.

1422
01:31:24,680 --> 01:31:26,620
To you...

1423
01:31:28,660 --> 01:31:30,630
I think I did my best.

1424
01:31:31,330 --> 01:31:33,500
Even if our choices don't align,

1425
01:31:34,170 --> 01:31:36,570
I wanted to tell you that.

1426
01:31:43,080 --> 01:31:44,462
It was Gyu Ri.

1427
01:31:44,462 --> 01:31:45,882
Nothing changed.

1428
01:31:45,882 --> 01:31:49,330
People haven't shifted
since halfway through.

1429
01:31:49,330 --> 01:31:51,130
That's usually the case.

1430
01:31:51,130 --> 01:31:54,360
Seo Won might have thought
she looked less steady.

1431
01:31:54,360 --> 01:31:57,280
- She felt so unsteady.
- Right.

1432
01:31:57,280 --> 01:31:59,820
In comparison, So Yun is tough.

1433
01:31:59,820 --> 01:32:02,150
Yes. She always does her thing.
But he's wrong.

1434
01:32:02,150 --> 01:32:05,250
That's why So Yun said that at the end.

1435
01:32:05,250 --> 01:32:06,980
She wished she joked around less.

1436
01:32:06,980 --> 01:32:08,990
[So sad]

1437
01:32:08,990 --> 01:32:11,560
[Jeong Gyu Ri's final choice]

1438
01:32:12,250 --> 01:32:18,070
[Seo Won was always there]

1439
01:32:19,370 --> 01:32:25,000
[Wu Yeol was somewhere
in the corner of her mind]

1440
01:32:27,450 --> 01:32:29,420
It could be Wu Yeol.

1441
01:32:31,110 --> 01:32:32,710
It's Seo Won.

1442
01:32:33,430 --> 01:32:34,970
Hello?

1443
01:32:34,970 --> 01:32:36,410
Hi.

1444
01:32:37,290 --> 01:32:40,100
[Who is it?]

1445
01:32:40,100 --> 01:32:45,100
[Jeong Gyu Ri's final choice Kim Seo Won]

1446
01:32:50,140 --> 01:32:52,300
It's cold. Hurry up.

1447
01:32:52,970 --> 01:32:55,010
Okay, I'm on my way.

1448
01:32:55,740 --> 01:32:59,140
- Hurry up.
- Okay, I will.

1449
01:32:59,140 --> 01:33:01,960
[Jeong Gyu Ri chose Kim Seo Won]

1450
01:33:01,960 --> 01:33:04,210
Gyu Ri recognized Seo Won.

1451
01:33:09,040 --> 01:33:11,620
Who is Jun Hyeon's final choice?

1452
01:33:13,570 --> 01:33:16,690
- I want to know what he'll say.
- Yes.

1453
01:33:18,430 --> 01:33:21,960
[He was steadfast with his feelings for her]

1454
01:33:21,960 --> 01:33:24,050
Seriously...

1455
01:33:28,730 --> 01:33:30,460
[Let's go, Yu Gyeong]

1456
01:33:30,460 --> 01:33:33,530
Everyone looks good with one another.

1457
01:33:34,560 --> 01:33:36,970
What will he say?

1458
01:33:37,620 --> 01:33:40,410
[Is his heart facing
the same direction today?]

1459
01:33:40,410 --> 01:33:42,060
Hello?

1460
01:33:42,060 --> 01:33:43,820
Hello?

1461
01:33:44,840 --> 01:33:46,990
It's so cold, Yu Gyeong.

1462
01:33:46,990 --> 01:33:50,860
[Jeong Jun Hyeon's final choice
is Kang Yu Gyeong]

1463
01:33:50,860 --> 01:33:54,920
Jun Hyeon's final choice is Yu Gyeong.

1464
01:33:55,660 --> 01:34:00,160
My final choice is you.

1465
01:34:05,070 --> 01:34:10,770
Thank you. This was more fun because of you.

1466
01:34:18,030 --> 01:34:20,840
- "1:05." That's my favorite song.
- Really?

1467
01:34:20,840 --> 01:34:23,230
It was hard for him to say that.

1468
01:34:23,230 --> 01:34:25,920
They had great conversations.

1469
01:34:25,920 --> 01:34:28,460
Look at this.

1470
01:34:29,460 --> 01:34:32,100
[He wanted to make her laugh]

1471
01:34:32,100 --> 01:34:35,150
"They chose each other."

1472
01:34:35,150 --> 01:34:39,760
[He gave his heart to one person]

1473
01:34:39,760 --> 01:34:43,320
- Expect more.
- Really?

1474
01:34:44,010 --> 01:34:47,860
Thanks to you, this was exciting. I had fun.

1475
01:34:51,140 --> 01:34:52,810
Me, too.

1476
01:34:52,810 --> 01:34:54,340
I mean it.

1477
01:34:55,550 --> 01:34:58,720
Thank you for liking me.

1478
01:35:08,670 --> 01:35:11,910
Wow! He hung up without saying
anything unnecessary.

1479
01:35:11,910 --> 01:35:13,630
[So into him]

1480
01:35:21,240 --> 01:35:23,580
I've never seen that face on him before.

1481
01:35:23,580 --> 01:35:26,490
He's holding it in.

1482
01:35:26,490 --> 01:35:31,060
Jun Hyeon's final choice is Yu Gyeong.

1483
01:35:31,060 --> 01:35:32,810
Tsuki, are you crying again?

1484
01:35:32,810 --> 01:35:34,680
Look this way. I want to tease you.

1485
01:35:34,680 --> 01:35:37,110
- Today is so legendary.
- Are you here to cry?

1486
01:35:37,110 --> 01:35:40,700
We've been seeing them for almost two months!

1487
01:35:40,700 --> 01:35:42,760
You're not as puffy today.

1488
01:35:42,760 --> 01:35:45,520
Really. Wow, my eyes are so legend.

1489
01:35:45,520 --> 01:35:49,420
I mean, I can't fathom...

1490
01:35:49,420 --> 01:35:52,270
She said "legendo."

1491
01:35:52,270 --> 01:35:57,000
She said it the way she does back home.

1492
01:35:57,000 --> 01:35:59,630
It's because I'm so moved.

1493
01:35:59,630 --> 01:36:01,310
Tsuki, why are you crying?

1494
01:36:01,310 --> 01:36:05,110
- How can you not feel this?
- Just tell us.

1495
01:36:05,110 --> 01:36:07,970
Tell us, legendo.

1496
01:36:07,970 --> 01:36:10,160
Then, Oppa...

1497
01:36:10,160 --> 01:36:13,930
Think of Jun Hyeon and Yu Gyeong's dates.

1498
01:36:13,930 --> 01:36:17,580
Think of all the time they had together.
And their last phone call.

1499
01:36:17,580 --> 01:36:22,710
They only said what they needed and hung up.

1500
01:36:22,710 --> 01:36:25,140
- I'm sorry.
- Do you not feel anything?

1501
01:36:25,140 --> 01:36:27,440
You write songs with AI, right?

1502
01:36:27,440 --> 01:36:30,260
[I think so... Gemi Roy]

1503
01:36:30,260 --> 01:36:31,330
Gosh...

1504
01:36:31,330 --> 01:36:34,930
It's not easy to be like that.
He likes her so much.

1505
01:36:34,930 --> 01:36:39,290
You could try to convince her,
say more words, sentences.

1506
01:36:39,290 --> 01:36:42,800
But he doesn't want to pressure
her even to the end.

1507
01:36:42,800 --> 01:36:45,470
He just said what he needed to and hung up.

1508
01:36:45,470 --> 01:36:47,630
- It was cool the way he hung up.
- Without saying extra words.

1509
01:36:47,630 --> 01:36:48,620
He's so cool.

1510
01:36:48,620 --> 01:36:51,710
I think he was choking up.

1511
01:36:51,710 --> 01:36:54,640
- We've never seen that look on his face.
- Right.

1512
01:36:54,640 --> 01:36:57,800
His eyes looked different.

1513
01:36:57,800 --> 01:36:58,710
Right.

1514
01:36:58,710 --> 01:37:02,220
Next up, Wu Yeol's final choice.

1515
01:37:02,220 --> 01:37:05,300
We're finally here.

1516
01:37:05,300 --> 01:37:09,650
[Park Wu Yeol's final choice]

1517
01:37:18,690 --> 01:37:20,990
[At times, he was awkward and not so smooth]

1518
01:37:21,680 --> 01:37:25,490
[But his feelings grew fiercely
and passionately]

1519
01:37:25,490 --> 01:37:27,910
Right, he changed a lot.

1520
01:37:29,470 --> 01:37:34,360
He went from the smoothest
to the most innocent.

1521
01:37:34,360 --> 01:37:37,030
[He wants to say his true feelings now]

1522
01:37:37,030 --> 01:37:38,830
Here he goes.

1523
01:37:38,830 --> 01:37:41,570
[Let's go, Wu Yeol]

1524
01:37:42,270 --> 01:37:44,120
[So nervous]

1525
01:37:55,440 --> 01:37:57,390
Crazy.

1526
01:37:57,390 --> 01:37:58,890
Let's go.

1527
01:37:58,890 --> 01:38:01,160
[It's Yu Gyeong for Wu Yeol]

1528
01:38:01,160 --> 01:38:03,560
He can relax now.

1529
01:38:14,980 --> 01:38:16,530
Hello?

1530
01:38:16,530 --> 01:38:22,100
[Park Wu Yeol's final choice
is Kang Yu Gyeong]

1531
01:38:22,630 --> 01:38:24,520
[Park Wu Yeol chose Kang Yu Gyeong]

1532
01:38:24,520 --> 01:38:28,030
Wu Yeol's final choice is Yu Gyeong.

1533
01:38:28,030 --> 01:38:32,280
Yu Gyeong is the lead in a drama.

1534
01:38:32,280 --> 01:38:33,730
[So sweet]

1535
01:38:36,140 --> 01:38:37,700
You know...

1536
01:38:39,020 --> 01:38:41,240
for the past month,

1537
01:38:45,020 --> 01:38:48,430
it's been fun to be with you.

1538
01:38:51,750 --> 01:38:54,890
Thank you for treating me as you are.

1539
01:38:54,890 --> 01:38:59,350
Thanks to you, I was able to be honest

1540
01:39:00,680 --> 01:39:02,590
with you.

1541
01:39:03,610 --> 01:39:06,560
My final choice...

1542
01:39:09,090 --> 01:39:10,670
is you.

1543
01:39:15,100 --> 01:39:16,990
[Choking up]

1544
01:39:19,440 --> 01:39:22,200
[Crying]

1545
01:39:22,200 --> 01:39:23,950
Everyone is crying!

1546
01:39:23,950 --> 01:39:25,460
He's over.

1547
01:39:25,460 --> 01:39:28,420
- Legendo.
- Legendo.

1548
01:39:32,310 --> 01:39:34,070
Thank you.

1549
01:39:36,830 --> 01:39:39,220
I called you to tell you that.

1550
01:39:40,720 --> 01:39:43,340
Thank you for calling me.

1551
01:39:44,480 --> 01:39:46,830
[A nervous confession]

1552
01:39:46,830 --> 01:39:51,800
[Did it reach Yu Gyeong's heart?]

1553
01:39:56,380 --> 01:39:58,290
[Crying]

1554
01:39:58,290 --> 01:40:01,420
I thought you were doing a press conference.

1555
01:40:01,420 --> 01:40:04,140
A press conference post-scandal.

1556
01:40:04,140 --> 01:40:05,540
Looks familiar.

1557
01:40:05,540 --> 01:40:09,240
Tsuki, you cried while
empathizing with Yu Gyeong.

1558
01:40:09,240 --> 01:40:11,260
Sang Min, you were feeling Wu Yeol.

1559
01:40:11,260 --> 01:40:13,030
You changed, too.

1560
01:40:13,030 --> 01:40:17,160
- A changed love.
- Because your wife changed you.

1561
01:40:17,160 --> 01:40:18,820
This is the final moment.

1562
01:40:18,820 --> 01:40:22,210
The moment where you say
your unwavering feelings.

1563
01:40:22,210 --> 01:40:24,850
I think my icy heart just melted.

1564
01:40:24,850 --> 01:40:28,460
We were concerned until the end.

1565
01:40:28,460 --> 01:40:31,100
You didn't have to take off your glasses.

1566
01:40:31,100 --> 01:40:33,700
Yes, you're right.

1567
01:40:33,700 --> 01:40:36,080
If you wear them for a long time...

1568
01:40:36,080 --> 01:40:38,510
Let's go to Yu Gyeong now.

1569
01:40:38,510 --> 01:40:41,330
- I'll be so happy watching this.
- Who is Yu Gyeong's final choice?

1570
01:40:41,330 --> 01:40:43,650
[Kang Yu Gyeong's final choice]

1571
01:40:50,580 --> 01:40:56,160
[She loved and was loved with all her heart]

1572
01:40:58,550 --> 01:41:00,550
[So many questions asked...]

1573
01:41:01,630 --> 01:41:02,990
[in the journey to find love]

1574
01:41:05,180 --> 01:41:10,080
[Who is at the end of those questions?]

1575
01:41:16,400 --> 01:41:17,930
Hello?

1576
01:41:17,930 --> 01:41:19,360
What?

1577
01:41:19,360 --> 01:41:22,230
- That scared me!
- Come on...

1578
01:41:22,230 --> 01:41:25,300
- We fell for it.
- I was about to scream.

1579
01:41:25,300 --> 01:41:27,920
I was so shocked.

1580
01:41:27,920 --> 01:41:29,530
Hello?

1581
01:41:30,510 --> 01:41:34,330
[To where did Yu Gyeong's heart turn to?]

1582
01:41:37,480 --> 01:41:39,000
Oppa.

1583
01:41:40,730 --> 01:41:42,780
[It's here!]

1584
01:41:42,780 --> 01:41:44,520
[Trying to be calm]

1585
01:41:46,600 --> 01:41:48,160
Oppa.

1586
01:41:49,200 --> 01:41:57,200
[Kang Yu Gyeong's final choice
is Park Wu Yeol]

1587
01:41:58,700 --> 01:42:02,110
[Kang Yu Gyeong chose Park Wu Yeol]

1588
01:42:02,110 --> 01:42:05,310
Yu Gyeong's final choice
is Wu Yeol, of course.

1589
01:42:05,310 --> 01:42:07,890
This was some crazy drama.

1590
01:42:07,890 --> 01:42:10,380
They're so cute together.

1591
01:42:13,000 --> 01:42:15,800
I thought I knew what to say.

1592
01:42:19,620 --> 01:42:21,440
Um...

1593
01:42:26,840 --> 01:42:33,840
In any case, I think it's you for me.

1594
01:42:35,180 --> 01:42:38,420
- It's like song lyrics.
- "In any case, I think it's you for me."

1595
01:42:38,420 --> 01:42:40,390
[Chin up because eyes
are swelling with tears]

1596
01:42:40,390 --> 01:42:47,550
In any case, I think it's you for me.

1597
01:42:51,150 --> 01:42:57,560
I thought about it so much
and debated this a lot.

1598
01:42:57,560 --> 01:43:00,430
And I was in denial, too.

1599
01:43:02,520 --> 01:43:04,660
But you're the one

1600
01:43:06,420 --> 01:43:11,460
who is on my mind the most.

1601
01:43:16,770 --> 01:43:19,960
Thanks to you...

1602
01:43:21,890 --> 01:43:24,740
I had so much fun.

1603
01:43:24,740 --> 01:43:27,070
It was exciting.

1604
01:43:27,070 --> 01:43:31,410
It was annoying. I was jealous and mad.

1605
01:43:32,730 --> 01:43:34,740
That's how I felt.

1606
01:43:39,550 --> 01:43:44,750
I think I came here
to discover those feelings.

1607
01:43:44,750 --> 01:43:47,360
That's why I'm calling you.

1608
01:43:52,720 --> 01:43:54,350
Thank you.

1609
01:43:56,730 --> 01:43:58,950
Hurry up.

1610
01:43:58,950 --> 01:44:00,630
I will.

1611
01:44:03,570 --> 01:44:06,620
I never even cry watching dramas!

1612
01:44:06,620 --> 01:44:08,400
[Bursting into tears]

1613
01:44:08,400 --> 01:44:10,010
[Chaos]

1614
01:44:10,010 --> 01:44:13,460
You have to watch him run!

1615
01:44:13,460 --> 01:44:16,960
[Wu Yeol was Yu Gyeong's answer]

1616
01:44:48,810 --> 01:44:50,610
What are you doing? It's cold.

1617
01:44:50,610 --> 01:44:51,950
What do you mean?

1618
01:44:51,950 --> 01:44:54,120
- Were you waiting?
- Yes.

1619
01:44:54,120 --> 01:44:55,640
- I ran.
- Really?

1620
01:44:55,640 --> 01:44:57,440
I really ran.

1621
01:45:08,010 --> 01:45:09,620
I missed you.

1622
01:45:10,340 --> 01:45:12,360
Same.

1623
01:45:20,580 --> 01:45:22,140
Thank you.

1624
01:45:22,910 --> 01:45:24,750
Thank you.

1625
01:45:26,080 --> 01:45:27,740
I like you.

1626
01:45:40,960 --> 01:45:42,780
Actually...

1627
01:45:45,350 --> 01:45:47,730
I like you, too.

1628
01:45:47,730 --> 01:45:49,200
Oh, my.

1629
01:45:52,290 --> 01:45:54,690
It's so nice out.

1630
01:45:57,730 --> 01:46:01,030
- You guys can hug! You're a couple now!
- I know!

1631
01:46:17,530 --> 01:46:21,060
Am I shaking from the cold or...

1632
01:46:21,060 --> 01:46:22,820
I don't know.

1633
01:46:37,940 --> 01:46:39,720
I like you.

1634
01:46:39,720 --> 01:46:41,910
I like you more.

1635
01:46:43,500 --> 01:46:45,970
- Where is the drone?
- This is crazy!

1636
01:46:45,970 --> 01:46:47,840
[Show us more!]

1637
01:46:47,840 --> 01:46:49,890
Get them from the front!

1638
01:46:49,890 --> 01:46:51,880
Tsuki is crying again!

1639
01:46:51,880 --> 01:46:55,550
[This is why this is my favorite dating show]

1640
01:46:55,550 --> 01:46:57,880
Where did the drone go?

1641
01:46:58,600 --> 01:47:02,060
[Wow! Finally!]

1642
01:47:10,080 --> 01:47:12,010
I like you.

1643
01:47:12,010 --> 01:47:14,200
I like you more.

1644
01:47:19,120 --> 01:47:21,420
Are you serious?

1645
01:47:27,670 --> 01:47:29,620
Thanks for hanging in there.

1646
01:47:36,380 --> 01:47:43,380
[They found each other in the end]

1647
01:47:43,990 --> 01:47:45,940
They won.

1648
01:47:45,940 --> 01:47:47,990
Standing ovation.

1649
01:47:47,990 --> 01:47:50,070
Thanks for hanging in there.

1650
01:47:50,070 --> 01:47:52,920
Oh, my. She hit his back.

1651
01:47:52,920 --> 01:47:55,020
Good job.

1652
01:47:55,020 --> 01:47:56,480
Wu Yeol, why did you make us go through that?

1653
01:47:56,480 --> 01:47:59,700
- He must've wanted to hug her so bad.
- I know.

1654
01:47:59,700 --> 01:48:04,470
I really want to thank Yu Gyeong because...

1655
01:48:04,470 --> 01:48:10,090
In all her struggles, her feelings
for Wu Yeol didn't change.

1656
01:48:10,090 --> 01:48:13,160
- That's why we're crying.
- I know.

1657
01:48:13,160 --> 01:48:17,660
I think this was the hardest romance.

1658
01:48:17,660 --> 01:48:21,920
Such devotion, especially from the girl.

1659
01:48:21,920 --> 01:48:25,150
The popular guy had to look around a bit,

1660
01:48:25,150 --> 01:48:29,250
- but he recognized her devotion later.
- Right.

1661
01:48:29,250 --> 01:48:32,320
Then he ran to her passionately
and said, "It's you."

1662
01:48:32,320 --> 01:48:34,140
It's a simple story...

1663
01:48:34,140 --> 01:48:38,180
Which is why it's rare. It's a fantasy.

1664
01:48:38,180 --> 01:48:40,650
- I can't believe it.
- What I loved seeing was...

1665
01:48:40,650 --> 01:48:44,850
I admire these young people
protecting their hearts,

1666
01:48:44,850 --> 01:48:52,030
even when they might get hurt,
bruised, or stepped on.

1667
01:48:52,030 --> 01:48:58,710
I hope the viewers can continue
rooting for them as well.

1668
01:48:58,710 --> 01:49:03,700
Since they're my age, I found
myself invested in them.

1669
01:49:03,700 --> 01:49:09,340
I cried so much at the end,
but I learned so much from it.

1670
01:49:09,340 --> 01:49:10,960
I loved it.

1671
01:49:10,960 --> 01:49:14,760
In the past, I enjoyed watching relationships
develop as if I were spying.

1672
01:49:14,760 --> 01:49:20,180
But this season made me reflect
on my relationships.

1673
01:49:20,180 --> 01:49:24,900
It was quite deep.

1674
01:49:24,900 --> 01:49:28,030
Every time I watched them, I choked up.

1675
01:49:28,030 --> 01:49:33,230
I feel like they filled the gaps in my 20s.

1676
01:49:33,230 --> 01:49:36,410
It was that moving for me. I'm so grateful.

1677
01:49:36,410 --> 01:49:40,860
I think you were more invested
than in past seasons, Eana.

1678
01:49:40,860 --> 01:49:43,880
Sadly, this is where we must say goodbye.

1679
01:49:43,880 --> 01:49:46,700
Thank you for watching until the end.

1680
01:49:46,700 --> 01:49:50,100
The most entertaining suspense, Heart Signal.

1681
01:49:50,100 --> 01:49:55,330
Thank you, everyone! Bye!

1682
01:49:55,330 --> 01:49:57,800
[Epilogue to continue]

1683
01:49:57,800 --> 01:50:00,610
[Welcoming the first snow together]

1684
01:50:00,610 --> 01:50:02,930
- It's our first group photo.
- Right?

1685
01:50:02,930 --> 01:50:05,070
February 1st.

1686
01:50:05,070 --> 01:50:08,140
February 1st...

1687
01:50:08,140 --> 01:50:13,130
[They laughed and cried together]

1688
01:50:13,830 --> 01:50:16,360
[25 unforgettable nights]

1689
01:50:16,360 --> 01:50:19,540
Everyone said that. Am I scary?

1690
01:50:20,310 --> 01:50:24,200
Because you wear your hair like that,

1691
01:50:24,200 --> 01:50:27,400
and you wear a suit.
No one else is like that.

1692
01:50:27,400 --> 01:50:30,880
I don't think Yu Gyeong likes suits.

1693
01:50:30,880 --> 01:50:33,950
I don't think that's her preference.

1694
01:50:33,950 --> 01:50:35,720
Oppa!

1695
01:50:35,720 --> 01:50:37,160
[Grins]

1696
01:50:37,160 --> 01:50:40,540
[Jun Hyeon started
dressing casually that day]

1697
01:50:40,540 --> 01:50:44,130
- What are you doing there?
- I'm cold.

1698
01:50:45,340 --> 01:50:46,180
What's this?

1699
01:50:46,180 --> 01:50:49,370
I wear suits every day.

1700
01:50:49,370 --> 01:50:52,310
But I tried not to here.

1701
01:50:55,730 --> 01:50:58,300
I was certain it was Yu Gyeong.

1702
01:50:58,300 --> 01:50:59,800
I was 100% sure.

1703
01:50:59,800 --> 01:51:03,820
I tend to trust people easily. That's why...

1704
01:51:04,580 --> 01:51:06,730
- I can see that.
- Yes.

1705
01:51:06,730 --> 01:51:10,160
She has such a good heart.

1706
01:51:10,160 --> 01:51:12,460
She's trusting.

1707
01:51:12,460 --> 01:51:14,760
That's how it started...

1708
01:51:14,760 --> 01:51:19,280
and I think my feelings grew.

1709
01:51:19,280 --> 01:51:20,530
[Nom]

1710
01:51:21,930 --> 01:51:23,640
You can have all of it.

1711
01:51:24,660 --> 01:51:27,220
You know when you just laugh like a fool?

1712
01:51:27,220 --> 01:51:29,290
[He couldn't hide his feelings]

1713
01:51:29,290 --> 01:51:32,550
Looking back,
I think I kept laughing like that.

1714
01:51:33,400 --> 01:51:37,790
In a way, Yu Gyeong...

1715
01:51:39,200 --> 01:51:42,680
made me nervous as if I was in my early 20s.

1716
01:51:42,680 --> 01:51:49,160
She made me want to look cool for her.

1717
01:51:49,160 --> 01:51:53,340
- I used to be really into plants.
- Really? Why?

1718
01:51:53,340 --> 01:51:56,490
[She remembered what he said in passing]

1719
01:51:56,490 --> 01:51:59,030
[And gifted him a plant]

1720
01:51:59,030 --> 01:52:02,170
- Didn't you say you have plants?
- I do.

1721
01:52:02,170 --> 01:52:04,360
I want you to look at this and cheer up.

1722
01:52:04,360 --> 01:52:06,170
- I was so grateful.
- Take good care of it.

1723
01:52:06,170 --> 01:52:11,550
The kind of gratitude "thank you"
can't cover sometimes.

1724
01:52:11,550 --> 01:52:13,290
This is...

1725
01:52:14,890 --> 01:52:18,860
It's at the clinic. I water it.

1726
01:52:18,860 --> 01:52:22,310
I think Min Ju.

1727
01:52:22,310 --> 01:52:25,730
That's who I keep thinking about.

1728
01:52:26,730 --> 01:52:29,780
I always make my bed.

1729
01:52:29,780 --> 01:52:33,510
But when I glanced into the guys' rooms,

1730
01:52:34,270 --> 01:52:38,380
Seong Min's bed was always made.

1731
01:52:39,220 --> 01:52:45,870
Seeing that, I felt like I understood
why I was attracted to him.

1732
01:52:45,870 --> 01:52:49,630
He tries to live an upright life.

1733
01:52:49,630 --> 01:52:54,160
He tries his best at everything in life.

1734
01:52:54,160 --> 01:52:57,690
That was attractive to me.

1735
01:52:57,690 --> 01:52:59,760
I like that song, "Hollywood"
by The Black Skirts.

1736
01:52:59,760 --> 01:53:01,520
"Hollywood"?

1737
01:53:02,950 --> 01:53:04,940
- This is it, right?
- Crazy.

1738
01:53:06,320 --> 01:53:10,040
Whenever we were carpooling...

1739
01:53:10,980 --> 01:53:12,740
I love it.

1740
01:53:12,740 --> 01:53:15,590
When we were at the beach, or on dates...

1741
01:53:15,590 --> 01:53:18,650
I will never forget this song.

1742
01:53:18,650 --> 01:53:22,310
He always played "Hollywood" for me.

1743
01:53:24,430 --> 01:53:29,170
I don't know. My feelings didn't end easily.

1744
01:53:30,010 --> 01:53:32,210
I keep wanting to see him.

1745
01:53:32,210 --> 01:53:37,700
When he's less busy,
I want to see him and talk.

1746
01:53:40,550 --> 01:53:44,290
- The beans are so good.
- You like beans?

1747
01:53:44,290 --> 01:53:46,490
You don't, do you?

1748
01:53:46,490 --> 01:53:48,620
I'll try to.

1749
01:53:48,620 --> 01:53:49,610
[Dizzy]

1750
01:53:53,530 --> 01:53:56,240
Why are you laughing? Do I look funny?

1751
01:53:56,240 --> 01:53:58,480
You make me laugh.

1752
01:53:59,840 --> 01:54:01,880
Seriously?

1753
01:54:01,880 --> 01:54:05,110
I couldn't breathe. It was so embarrassing.

1754
01:54:05,110 --> 01:54:07,940
It was the most heart-fluttering
moment of my life.

1755
01:54:07,940 --> 01:54:09,790
My heart ached.

1756
01:54:09,790 --> 01:54:13,410
She looks cold, like she's just saying stuff.

1757
01:54:13,410 --> 01:54:15,430
But she means everything.

1758
01:54:16,430 --> 01:54:20,720
I could see the warmhearted,
fragile young girl in her.

1759
01:54:20,720 --> 01:54:21,980
So Yun is so feminine.

1760
01:54:21,980 --> 01:54:25,250
For sure. You're not just a softie.
You're smooth.

1761
01:54:25,250 --> 01:54:27,170
Why do you think that?

1762
01:54:27,170 --> 01:54:29,230
I can just tell.

1763
01:54:29,230 --> 01:54:30,920
Do you prefer feminine or tough women?

1764
01:54:30,920 --> 01:54:33,640
I totally prefer feminine, for sure.

1765
01:54:35,380 --> 01:54:36,850
I like that.

1766
01:54:39,690 --> 01:54:41,880
She laughed a lot at that.

1767
01:54:41,880 --> 01:54:44,340
Smiling with her eyes.

1768
01:54:45,140 --> 01:54:47,310
You smiled as soon as you sat down.

1769
01:54:47,310 --> 01:54:51,070
There was one person smiling with her eyes.

1770
01:54:51,070 --> 01:54:55,560
[The only person who noticed her]

1771
01:54:55,560 --> 01:55:00,690
I never thought I had a pretty smile.

1772
01:55:00,690 --> 01:55:03,660
I like hearing that I have a pretty smile.

1773
01:55:03,660 --> 01:55:06,630
Seo Won told me that a lot.

1774
01:55:06,630 --> 01:55:08,680
It made me so happy.

1775
01:55:10,590 --> 01:55:13,520
I really fell for Seo Won.

1776
01:55:13,520 --> 01:55:16,640
I kept thinking about what
it would be like post-show.

1777
01:55:16,640 --> 01:55:21,800
This is a secret, but I thought
we might work out, so...

1778
01:55:21,800 --> 01:55:25,300
I looked up our compatibility chart.

1779
01:55:25,300 --> 01:55:26,640
So pretty.

1780
01:55:26,640 --> 01:55:27,840
[Surprised]

1781
01:55:27,840 --> 01:55:29,790
The photo.

1782
01:55:29,790 --> 01:55:31,560
- Hey!
- It's good.

1783
01:55:31,560 --> 01:55:35,300
[Her feelings grew and deepened]

1784
01:55:35,300 --> 01:55:38,690
I think I decide in the first 3 seconds.

1785
01:55:38,690 --> 01:55:41,710
But here, I changed my mind on that.

1786
01:55:41,710 --> 01:55:44,530
I think you have to give people time.

1787
01:55:44,530 --> 01:55:51,420
I realized love isn't determined
by a single moment.

1788
01:55:51,420 --> 01:55:53,550
[The daily lives of the residents
after Signal House]

1789
01:55:53,550 --> 01:55:55,940
[I was so happy to be
with the amazing cast and crew]

1790
01:55:55,940 --> 01:55:58,760
[Thank you to everyone
who rooted for me - Jun Hyeon]

1791
01:56:01,080 --> 01:56:03,460
[Looking back, every moment was a gift]

1792
01:56:03,460 --> 01:56:06,380
[Thank you for laughing and
commiserating with me... - Seong Min]

1793
01:56:08,970 --> 01:56:11,740
[There are no right answers in love,
but we are discovering them as we write...]

1794
01:56:11,740 --> 01:56:14,320
[Thank you for reading the
sentences we are writing - Min Ju]

1795
01:56:17,100 --> 01:56:19,290
[Thank you for laughing and crying
with us, for rooting for us]

1796
01:56:19,290 --> 01:56:21,510
[I was so happy, thanks to you.
I love you. - Seo Won]

1797
01:56:24,100 --> 01:56:26,430
[Through Heart Signal, I learned more
about love and what I was lacking]

1798
01:56:26,430 --> 01:56:28,900
[Thank you for rooting for us
and for the love - So Yun]

1799
01:56:28,900 --> 01:56:41,000
[Precious relationships continue
in their daily lives]

1800
01:56:41,000 --> 01:56:50,700
[They're in different places,
but it's still nice to see their faces]

1801
01:56:50,700 --> 01:56:58,150
[And their stories are still not over]

1802
01:56:58,690 --> 01:57:04,920
This morning, I dropped off
Yu Gyeong on my way to work.

1803
01:57:04,920 --> 01:57:08,640
I was thinking about her.

1804
01:57:11,460 --> 01:57:15,200
Seeing Yu Gyeong smile

1805
01:57:15,200 --> 01:57:19,730
makes me happy, too.

1806
01:57:20,760 --> 01:57:24,320
She's the one who excites me the most.

1807
01:57:24,320 --> 01:57:28,020
I feel the most at ease around her.

1808
01:57:28,020 --> 01:57:33,230
The person who changed me the most
is Yu Gyeong.

1809
01:57:33,230 --> 01:57:38,810
She helped me see a new side
of myself I didn't know.

1810
01:57:41,780 --> 01:57:43,890
That's why it's Yu Gyeong.

1811
01:57:46,720 --> 01:57:53,450
You can't defeat the feelings
you have for someone here.

1812
01:57:54,550 --> 01:57:56,640
You just laugh.

1813
01:57:56,640 --> 01:57:59,980
You keep checking their face while on a date.

1814
01:57:59,980 --> 01:58:04,410
You can't believe that person is next to you.

1815
01:58:05,440 --> 01:58:10,160
You can't help what your heart wants.

1816
01:58:12,970 --> 01:58:17,320
I must've thought that Wu Yeol is
the one I'm supposed to be with.

1817
01:58:20,460 --> 01:58:24,800
There's one moment that I remember.

1818
01:58:24,800 --> 01:58:29,210
We were walking, and I looked at her.

1819
01:58:29,210 --> 01:58:32,750
In that moment, I felt it.

1820
01:58:33,670 --> 01:58:35,530
I just thought, "I like her."

1821
01:58:35,530 --> 01:58:37,850
I definitely like her.

1822
01:58:38,710 --> 01:58:41,190
I really like Yu Gyeong.

1823
01:58:46,140 --> 01:58:51,750
"I like you and want to see you seriously."

1824
01:58:51,750 --> 01:58:53,860
So, I was trying to say,
"I really like you, too."

1825
01:58:53,860 --> 01:58:55,700
Then, I tried to say "but..."

1826
01:58:55,700 --> 01:58:59,540
He said, "But what? If we like
each other, we can date!"

1827
01:58:59,540 --> 01:59:02,370
That's how it went.

1828
01:59:02,370 --> 01:59:07,290
I said, "This is how I feel,

1829
01:59:07,290 --> 01:59:09,910
and I want to see you seriously."

1830
01:59:13,180 --> 01:59:16,480
I also think we can date
if we like each other.

1831
01:59:18,255 --> 01:59:22,200
[That's how Yu Gyeong and Wu Yeol
became lovers]

1832
01:59:22,200 --> 01:59:25,520
[I got to know myself better,
thanks to these amazing people]

1833
01:59:25,520 --> 01:59:27,800
[Thank you for all your
amazing support - Yu Gyeong]

1834
01:59:27,800 --> 01:59:30,670
[I learned so much through
this precious experience]

1835
01:59:30,670 --> 01:59:33,170
[I will continue to be honest
and sincere - Wu Yeol]

1836
01:59:33,170 --> 01:59:39,410
[Their story began after the final choice]

1837
01:59:39,410 --> 01:59:42,770
[Yu Gyeong's favorite burger]

1838
01:59:42,770 --> 01:59:45,475
[They are sharing small
everyday moments together]

1839
01:59:45,475 --> 01:59:48,295
[The drive-through theater
that they promised to go to]

1840
01:59:52,505 --> 01:59:58,140
[Their feelings for each other
began with heart flutters]

1841
01:59:58,140 --> 02:00:03,150
[And it became love]

1842
02:01:08,620 --> 02:01:13,530
[Thank you for your love for Heart Signal 5]
